Kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse kw'ibyago by'indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza hagati ya 1 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abarwaye coronavirus (COVID-19) ugereranyije ugaragaza ko ibintu bimeze kimwe mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, ibyo bikaba byemeza ko nubwo biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirimo gutera imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Nk'uko byagenze mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane bigomba kwitegura kwiyongera kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bitaro bya ICU.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari umuntu umwe wanduye indwara y'ibihaha itagira icyorezo muri Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye iyo ndwara ari koronavirusi nshya ubu izwi nka SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara ya koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, hafi 80 ku ijana by'abantu banduye COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara y'ubuhumekero irimo cyangwa idafite ibicurane by'ibihaha, abenshi muri bo bakira.
Hafi 14 ku ijana by'abarwayi, COVID-19 ituma barwara cyane bigatuma bajya mu bitaro, mu gihe abasigaye 6 ku ijana barwara indwara ikomeye cyane igasaba kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa mu bitaro bazize COVID-19 ni 4% gusa.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twihaye gusuzuma uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwagiye bufata indi mibare muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza (Ubwongereza), tugereranyije n'uko byagenze mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi imibare y'abantu banduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'iy'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira, kandi uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gihagaze mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi muri iki gihe birimo gukurikira uko cyagenze muri icyo gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu igazeti ya Eurovigilance yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko abantu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi hakurikijwe ibisobanuro by'abanduye byatanzwe na OMS.
Mu karere ka EU/EEA, abanduye batatu ba mbere bemejwe batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse bavuye i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, hari abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 30 bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza (Ubwongereza), hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'iyo tariki, hari abantu 39,768 banduye na 1,727 bapfuye, muri bo 17,750 banduye na 1,441 bapfuye mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kubona imibare yose hamwe n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurinda no Gutegeka Indwara (ECDC), gitanga imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi yose, igaragazwa gusa n'ibitangazamakuru byemewe n'amategeko, urugero nk'inzego z'ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'uturere n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 yagiye igenda mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kugereranya n'ibyabaye mu Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo gusuzuma umubare w'abanduye COVID-19, twabaze umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 yose, dufatiye ku buryo COVID-19 yagiye igenda mu buryo bw'ibanze mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twagereranyije kandi imibare y'abarwayi bose muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani n'ibyavuye mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibereho ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imibare y'ibyumweru 14 by'abarwaye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza yagaragaje ko hari byinshi bitandukanye n'ibyabaye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, buza kwiyongera cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (amakuru y'inyongera).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'abanduye muri Italy, ariko ibindi bihugu byose byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'u Burayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza na byo byagize ukwiyongera nk'uko mu mubare w'abanduye COVID-19 (amakuru y'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare yose y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'ibyavuye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Byagaragaye ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza byari bimaze gutanga raporo y'umubare w'abanduye ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu bishize cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongera mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere y'ibyago byose bya COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo kirimo gutera imbere ku muvuduko ugereranywa mu bihugu byose.
Ibi kandi n'ubwo ibihugu bitandukanye biri mu byiciro bitandukanye kandi hakaba hari itandukaniro mu buryo inzego z'ubuzima z'igihugu zitabira, hashobora kuba hari itandukaniro mu bisobanuro by'abarwayi ndetse n'itandukaniro mu buryo bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bamenye niba barwaye COVID-19, harimo no gupimwa nyuma yo kwandura.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu duce tw'u Butaliyani twazahajwe na COVID-19 bavuze ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi barwaye COVID-19 bari bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane byo muri utwo duce byari bimaze kugera ku bushobozi bwabyo.
Amakuru ajyanye no kwinjiza abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane ubu aboneka mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA ku kigero cya 6% na 1% by'abarwayi (amakuru atatanzwe).
Icyakora, ni ngombwa ko hakorwa ikorwa ry'ibikoresho mu buryo buhoraho kugira ngo hakorwe ibisobanuro by'ibikoresho byo kugenzura biriho ubu byibanda ku mubare w'abanduye n'abapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 201011 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu mibare y'ibitanda biboneka mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe n'ubw'indembe mu Burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29,2 ku bantu 100,000 mu Budage kugeza ku bitanda 4,2 muri Portugal.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bifite ibikoresho byinshi cyangwa bike ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (ibitanda 12,5 byo mu bitaro byagutse n'ibisanzwe ku bantu 100,000 mu 201011).
Imiterere yo kugereranya ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi, hamwe n'ibyerekezo kuri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ku mubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro bafite ibyago 90% byo kurenga ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byo mu bitaro bya ICU, bitangwa mu ivugururwa rya gatandatu ry'igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago bya COVID-19 rya CEPCM.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abarwayi bari mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ibihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe bikunze kwakira abaturage bo mu karere, amakuru ku barwayi n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe by'indembe, byashyiriweho ku rwego rwa 2 rw'ibarura ry'ibice by'akarere (NUTS 2).
Ubumenyi bw'u Butaliyani n'ibyahindutse mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirimo gutera imbere mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane bigomba kwitegura ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomeza gukwirakwira mu baturage ndetse n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 wiyongera bagakenera kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bitaro bya ICU, nk'uko byagenze mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'isesengura ry'ibyago riherutse gukorwa na CEPCM, uburyo bwihuse, bwihuse kandi bunonosoye ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, buvuye ku buryo bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ku buryo bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira, kuko kwiyongera vuba kandi hakiri kare kw'umubare w'abanduye bishobora gutuma abashyiraho imyanzuro n'ibitaro badahabwa igihe gihagije cyo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no guhuza ibisubizo byabo, niba nta kintu cyakozwe mbere.
Igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago kandi rigaragaza ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari igihe gito buri gihugu gishobora kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 kugira ngo kigabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya ibibazo by'ubuzima.
Bitabaye ibyo, birashoboka ko inzego z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu bya EU/EEA zizahura n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19), iterwa na koronavirusi ya 2 y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS) (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3000 kandi cyanduye abantu barenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi, bituma habaho ibyago by'abantu.
Kimwe na SARS-CoV, yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi banduye SARS mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura binyuze mu ducurama kandi igatuma abantu bagaragaza ibimenyetso nk'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'ubukana buke ugereranyije na SARS, ariko yandura cyane, kandi yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato, kandi ikagira ingaruka nyinshi ku bagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare w'ibitabo byiyongera vuba kuri iyi ndwara iri kuvuka, iyi nkuru igerageza gutanga isuzuma ryuzuye kandi rikwiriye kuri iki kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi bukomeje kwiyongera.
Tuzaganira ku by'ibanze mu bijyanye n'icyorezo, indwara, virusi, gusuzuma indwara, kuvurwa, kugenzura no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikiriho bidasobanutse, twizeye ko iki kiganiro kizatuma dusobanukirwa neza iby'iyo ndwara ikomeye kandi tukayirandura.
Umunsi mukuru w'Igisibo wabaye ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020, wagize ingaruka ku Bashinwa, kuko bari baremerewe kuguma mu nzu mu gihe cy'icyumweru cy'izahabu ndetse no mu bindi byumweru birebire bitewe n'icyorezo gishya cya virusi.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na koronavirusi (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS) mu 2003; ni yo mpamvu yiswe SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, n'indwara ifitanye isano yitwa coronavirus disease 19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan, gikwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose vuba, kigafata n'ibindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yari imaze gutuma abantu barenga 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abarenga 40.000 barwariye mu bitaro naho abasaga 3.000 barapfuye.
OMS ivuga ko COVID-19 ari  umwanzi wa mbere w'abaturage , ushobora guteza akaga gakomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, inyandiko zisaga 200 z'ubushakashatsi kuri COVID-19 zanditswe, harimo mu bijyanye n'ubushakashatsi ku ndwara, indwara z'ibyorezo, indwara zitera indwara, gusuzuma no kuvura, kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yerekana uko virusi yagiye ikurikirana, yabonetse mu barwayi benshi.
Iyi raporo igerageza gusubiramo iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi kuri iki kibazo gishya kandi gikomeje kwiyongera.
Uko bishoboka kose, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara ya koronavirusi, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyabaye mu 2012).
Tuzongera turebe ibyo twize kugeza ubu mu bijyanye no kwirinda no kwitegura indwara, kandi tuganire ku bibazo bimwe na bimwe bikiri hanze ariko byihutirwa.
Koronavirusi isanzwe ifatwa nk'indwara zidakora ku bantu, ahanini zitera nibura 15% by'ibicurane 4.
Icyakora, muri iki kinyejana, twabonye koronavirusi ebyiri zandura cyane abantu, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye haduka icyorezo cyatangiye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, mbere yo gukwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi mu buryo bwihuse, kandi abantu benshi barwara kandi bagapfa.
COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya coronavirus mu mateka ya vuba aha.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho ya 1,1, mu gihe cy'ibanze, mu mujyi wa Wuhan, ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko habonetse indwara y'ibicurane itaramenyekana.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, urutonde rwa coronavirus rwaragaragaye.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wapfuye yabonetse mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyari cyahise gikwira mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu bituranye.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, byavuzwe ko hari abakozi bo mu buvuzi banduye, bikaba byerekana ko ubwandu bushobora gutandukana n'ubundi.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan washyizwe mu kato, imodoka zose zitwara abagenzi zihagarikwa.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe kuri iyi ndwara bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bari bahuye n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja ryo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, aho bivugwa ko ari ho indwara yaturutse, kandi ko itari iturutse ku nyamaswa.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi ku buzima ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, iyi ndwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo.2).2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka vuba, icyorezo n'uburemere bwacyo biracyari kugenzurwa.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakorewe mu bigo bitandukanye ku barwayi 8,866, barimo 4,021 banduye COVID-19, bwagaragaje uko icyorezo cyari giteye (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yandura abantu b'imyaka yose, ariko cyane cyane mu bafite hagati ya 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47,7%) cy'abanduye bari bafite imyaka irenga 50, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20, kandi 14 gusa bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yandura cyane abagabo (0,31/100 000) kurusha abagore (0,27/100 000).
