Izindi miti zihagarika ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri mu gihe cy'indwara z'ibyorezo birimo uburyo bwo guhindura ibisubizo by'umubiri n'utugingo ngengabuzima twa T, guhagarika cytokine IFN-γ, IL-1 na TNF, kubuza JAK, blinatumomab, cytokine 4 signaling suppressor na HDAC inhibitors.
Steroids, nk'imiti igabanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, zakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ibikomere by'ubuhumekero.
Icyakora, gufata siteroyide nyinshi nta ngaruka nziza byagize ku kwangirika kw'ibihaha bikomeye mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ahubwo, byateza ingaruka zikomeye zirimo uburwayi bw'amagufwa butuma umuntu atabasha kurwara indwara.
Icyakora, hatanzwe inama yo gukoresha corticosteroids z'inkingo ngufi z'ibipimo biri hagati y'ibyoroheje n'ibisanzwe mu buryo bwitondewe ku barwayi bafite COVID-19 ikomeye.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, nta muti wa virusi ushoboye kwemezwa.
Icyakora, imiti ya Remdesivir, ikoreshwa mu mitsi mu kuvura indwara ya COVID-19, yagaragaye ko ifasha cyane umurwayi wo muri Amerika.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya wa virusi watangijwe na Gilead mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi ya Ebola na Marburg.
Nyuma, Remdesivir yagaragaje ko ishobora no kubuza izindi virusi z'umugozi umwe wa RNA, harimo MERS na SARS.
Kubera ibyo bintu byavumbuwe, Gilead yoherereje iki cyuma Ubushinwa kugira ngo kijye kugeragezwa ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibisubizo byitezwe cyane.
Byongeye kandi, baricitinib, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir hamwe na ribavirin byashyizwe imbere nk'uburyo bwo kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bukabije.
Indwara y'umwijima, isesemi, gusubiranamo, kwangirika kw'umwijima n'ibindi bibazo bishobora guterwa no gufata imiti ivanze na lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Imikorere y'iyi miti hamwe n'indi miti ikoreshwa n'abarwayi igomba kugenzurwa neza.
Plasma y'abarwayi bakize n'imikorere y'abasirikare
Gukusanya amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara yandura kugira ngo bavurwe abandi barwayi bafite iyo ndwara cyangwa barinde abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza iyo ndwara ni umugenzo umaze igihe kirekire.
Ibi ni ukubera ko abarwayi bakize akenshi bagira umubare munini w'abasirikare b'umubiri barwanya indwara.
Imigera ni immunoglobuline (Ig) ikorwa n'utugingo ngengabuzima twa B kugira ngo turwanye udukoko dutera indwara n'utundi duce tw'amahanga; tumenya molekile zidasanzwe ziri mu ndwara kandi tukazica mu buryo butaziguye.
Ibipimo bya plasma byavanywe mu maraso y'itsinda ry'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze bihabwa abarwayi 10 barwaye cyane.
Ibimenyetso byabo byagiye bihinduka mu masaha 24, bifatanyije no kugabanuka kw'ubuhumekero, kugabanuka kw'ubwandu bwa virusi no kongera umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Ariko, hakenewe igenzura no gusobanura kugira ngo ubwo buryo buzashobore gutangwa ku buryo bukomeye kugeza igihe hatagize uburyo bwihariye bwo kuvura.
Ikindi kandi, kubera ingaruka z'ubuvuzi, hari ibyago bimwe na bimwe by'ibipimo bya plasma bikwiye gusuzumwa neza.
Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri bashobora gutuma umubiri urushaho gukora neza, bigatuma habaho indwara yo kugabanya imisemburo y'umubiri (syndrome de libération de cytokines), ishobora no guhitana umuntu.
Umubare w'abanduye mu maraso ubusanzwe uba ari muto, kandi plasma ikenerwa mu kuvura abarwayi barwaye cyane ni myinshi.
Biragoye guhanga no gukora abasirikare b'umubiri byihariye mu buryo bwihuse ku buryo bashobora kurwanya icyorezo cy'isi yose.
Ku bw'ibyo, ni ngombwa kandi ni byiza cyane gutandukanya insoro za B z'abarwayi bakize no kumenya kode z'imiterere z'abasirikare b'umubiri b'ingenzi cyangwa gushaka abasirikare b'umubiri bakomeye ku poroteyine z'ingenzi za virusi.
Ibi byatuma habaho kongera vuba ingano y'abanduye.
TCM yakoreshejwe mu Bushinwa mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye.
Ariko ingaruka zayo ahanini zishingiye ku guhuza ibintu byinshi mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'ubushakashatsi bushingiye ku bitekerezo bya TCM.
Ibyinshi mu bikoresho bifite akamaro biracyari bike cyangwa ntibimenyekane kuko bigoye kubikuramo no kubisuzuma, cyangwa kumenya imirwi myiza.
Kugeza ubu, kubera ko nta muti wihariye wa COVID-19 ufatika, TCM ni imwe mu miti y'ingenzi ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa byoroheje cyangwa barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Urugero, ingirabuzimafatizo za Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen zagaragaje ko zifasha mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibipimo byiza cyane byo gukira COVID-19 byabonetse mu ntara zo mu Bushinwa zakoresheje TCM ku barwayi 87% harimo Gansu (63,7%), Ningxia (50%) na Hunan (50%), mu gihe mu ntara ya Hubei hakoreshejwe TCM ku barwayi 30% gusa ba COVID-19, hakaba hari umubare muto cyane (13%).
Ariko kandi, uru ni urugero rugufi cyane kuko hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigira ingaruka, urugero nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'uburemere bw'indwara, bigomba kwitabwaho mu gusuzuma.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang na bagenzi be basohoye ubushakashatsi bwagereranyije uburyo bwo kuvura bukoresha imiti yo mu Burengerazuba (MO) gusa n'uburyo bwo kuvura buhuriweho bukoresha MO na TCM.
Byagaragaye ko igihe cyo kugaruka ku bushake ku bushake, igihe cyo guhosha ibimenyetso n'igihe cyo kujya mu bitaro byari bike cyane mu itsinda rya MO+MTC ugereranyije n'itsinda rya MO gusa.
Icy'ingenzi kurushaho, imibare y'ibyago byo kuremba (kuva ku boroheje kugeza ku bikomeye) yari hasi cyane mu itsinda rya MO+MTC ugereranyije n'iryo muri MO gusa (7.4% ugereranyije na 46.2%); kandi n'imfu zari hasi mu itsinda rya MO+MTC ugereranyije n'iryo muri MO gusa (8.8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Ariko kandi, ubufasha n'umutekano wa TCM biracyari ngombwa ko byemezwa binyuze mu igerageza rifite ububasha rikomeye kandi rifite ibigo byinshi.
Ni byiza kandi gusobanura uburyo bwo gukora no gusobanura neza ibice by'imiti ikoreshwa mu miti ya TCM cyangwa ifatanyije na yo, niba bishoboka.
Abantu bagaragaweho ko bashobora kuba baranduye cyangwa bafite COVID-19 bakunze guhangayikishwa cyane n'iyo ndwara yandura cyane kandi yica, kandi abajyanwa mu kato na bo bakunze kumva bababaye, bafite irungu n'uburakari.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'ubwandu, nk'umuriro, impiswi n'inkorora, hamwe n'ingaruka mbi z'imiti, nk'ibitotsi biterwa na corticosteroids, bishobora gutuma umuntu arushaho guhangayika no guhangayika mu mutwe.
Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo cya SARS, hari ibimenyetso byinshi by'indwara zo mu mutwe byatangajwe, harimo kwiheba, guhangayika, ubwoba, guhungabana mu mitekerereze, ibimenyetso by'indwara zo mu mutwe, guhungabana cyane ndetse no kwiyahura.
Gushakisha abantu bahuye n'indwara no kubajyana mu kato, nk'igice cy'igisubizo cy'inzego z'ubuzima muri rusange ku cyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abarwayi barushaho guhangayika no kwicira urubanza ku ngaruka z'ubwandu, kubajyana mu kato no gutesha agaciro imiryango yabo n'incuti zabo.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu barwaye COVID-19, abantu bagaragaweho ko bashobora kuba barwaye, abantu bahuye n'abo bantu, n'abandi bantu bose bari mu kaga, bagomba kwitabwaho mu by'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe.
Ubu bufasha mu by'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho amatsinda y'abantu benshi, gushyikirana neza no gutanga amakuru buri gihe kandi asobanutse ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n'imigambi y'ubuvuzi, no gukoresha porogaramu n'ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki by'umwuga kugira ngo umuntu yirinde guhura na mugenzi we.
Inkingo z'ingirakamaro ni ingenzi mu guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ibinyabuzima n'abantu zanduye zikajya ku bantu bafite ubwandu bworoshye, kandi akenshi zikoreshwa nk'inkunga mu kuvura virusi mu kurwanya ibyorezo biterwa na virusi zigezweho.
Hakozwe ingamba zo gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri poroteyine ya S, hagamijwe gukora abasirikare b'umubiri bakomeye bafasha mu gihe kirekire no/cyangwa gutuma umuntu agira ubudahangarwa bwo kurinda SARS-CoV.
Inkingo z'ubuzima zagabanutse zashyizwe mu igeragezwa mu nyamaswa ku bwandu bwa SARS.
Icyakora, ubushobozi bwa in vivo bw'izi nkingo zishobora gukoreshwa mu bantu bakuze no ku bantu bafite ubukana buhitana ndetse n'uburyo zirinda kwandura virusi ziterwa n'inyamaswa biracyari ngombwa kuko nta bushakashatsi bw'imiti bwakozwe.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS imaze imyaka 17 itakiriho kandi nta muntu mushya wigeze uvugwa.
Icyakora, hari izindi ndwara za MERS n'ibindi byorezo bikomeje kugaragara mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati no mu tundi duce bitewe n'uko hari ibyago byo kwandura mu duce twanduye.
Uburyo butandukanye bwo gukingira MERS bwakoreshejwe hakoreshejwe virusi itakoreshejwe, plasmide za DNA, utwo twuma dutwara virusi, utuntu duto duto, utwo twuma dufitanye isano na virusi n'utundi duce duto tw'imikorere y'indwara z'ibice by'ibinyabutabire, kandi bumwe muri bwo bwakozwe mu nyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2 rwizewe kandi rukora neza ku bantu batagira ubudahangarwa ni intego yihutirwa kandi y'ingenzi mu kurwanya icyorezo gikomeje.
Icyakora, iki ni ikibazo gikomeye kubera igihe kirekire (amezi 18 ku kigereranyo) gikenewe kugira ngo haboneke urukingo n'impinduka z'indwara za koronavirusi.
Kubera ko ari indwara nshya, COVID-19 iri mu nzira yo kuvura abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi.
Abenshi mu barwayi barakira buhoro buhoro nta ngaruka mbi.
Icyakora, kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 kandi ifitanye isano n'uburwayi bwinshi n'urupfu mu barwayi bakomeye.
Ku bw'ibyo, gushyiraho uburyo bwo kubara indwara ni ngombwa kugira ngo inzego z'ubuzima zishobore gushyira imbere serivisi, cyane cyane mu duce tudafite amikoro menshi.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kugeza ubu, ibintu bishobora kugira ingaruka cyangwa bifitanye isano n'uburwayi bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ni ibi bikurikira (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe33):
Imyaka: imyaka ni yo yari ifitanye isano cyane n'ubwandu bwa SARS, kandi bisa n'aho ari na yo ifitanye isano na COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane abantu bafite hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65, aho 47,7% muri bo bari hejuru y'imyaka 50 nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakorewe ku bantu 8,866, nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Abarwayi bari bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara ziterwa na yo n'ibibazo by'uburwayi, kandi bari bakuze cyane (imyaka 66 mu gihe bari mu kigero cy'imyaka 51), ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko imyaka ari yo ituma abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwara indwara.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abagabo benshi kurusha abagore (0,31/100 000 ugereranyije na 0,27/100 000), nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Indwara n'ibibazo: abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bashobora kurwara umutima cyane no kugira ibibazo by'umuvuduko w'amaraso.
Ibyabaye ku mutima nabyo ni byo byateye urupfu rw'abarwayi ba SARS.
Byagaragaye ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no guhuza n'utugingo ngengabuzima twa ACE2 twitwa cholangiocytes, ibyo bikaba bishobora gutuma impyiko zidakora neza ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ni ngombwa kumenya ko imyaka n'ubwandu bw'ibibazo by'ubuzima biri mu buryo bukomeye kandi bishobora guhungabanya.
Ibisubizo bidasanzwe bya laboratwari: igipimo cya poroteyine C-reactive (CRP) mu maraso kigaragaza uburemere bw'ubuhumekero cyangwa kwangirika kw'ingingo; byashyizwe imbere nk'ikimenyetso gishobora kwemeza indwara, gusubiza imiti no gukira.
Hari kandi ibitekerezo byatanzwe ku bijyanye n'isano riri hagati y'umubare wa CRP n'uburemere bwa COVID-19 ndetse n'uko ishobora kwandura.
Ikindi kandi, ibipimo byinshi bya lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), daspartate aminotransferase (AST), dalanine aminotransferase (ALT) na creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bishobora kugira uruhare mu gutuma umuntu arwara indwara.
Izi enzymes zigaragarira cyane mu ngingo nyinshi, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu kibyimba, kandi zisohoka iyo hari imvune mu ngingo.
Ni yo mpamvu mu buryo bwa gakondo ari ibimenyetso by'umutima cyangwa impyiko zidakora neza.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi: ibisubizo bya radiografi y'igituza n'igihe ibimenyetso by'uburwayi byamaze bigomba gusuzumwa hamwe n'ibindi bintu bigufasha kumenya uko COVID-19 ishobora kwibasira umuntu n'ibibazo by'uburwayi.
Gukoresha Steroids: Nkuko byavuzwe haruguru, Steroids ni imiti igabanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ikoreshwa cyane mu kwivuza indwara zandura mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'ibikomere by'ubuhumekero.
Kubera ko gukoresha ibipimo byinshi bya corticosteroids byakoreshejwe cyane mu barwayi ba SARS barembye, abenshi mu barokotse basanze bafite uburwayi bw'amagufa butuma batagira ubushobozi kandi ubuzima bwabo butagira agaciro.
Ku bw'ibyo, mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, gukoresha za siteroyide ku barwayi bafite COVID-19 bigomba kuba mu gipimo gito kandi mu gihe gito.
Imihangayiko yo mu mutwe: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo byinshi by'imihangayiko idasanzwe, akenshi abarwayi bakamara igihe kirekire mu kato, bahangayika cyane, ndetse n'ababo bapfuye cyangwa abandi barwayi.
Ni ngombwa gutanga ubufasha bw'imiti n'ubufasha bw'igihe kirekire kugira ngo aba bantu bashobore guhangana n'iyo mihangayiko no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku baturage kugeza ubu bugaragaza ko COVID-19 ifite ibimenyetso by'icyorezo bitandukanye n'iby'indwara ya SARS.
Uretse kuba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwiyongera mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, ishobora no kwiyongera neza mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru kandi ntihagire ibimenyetso cyangwa ibimenyetso byinshi mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubwandu, nk'uko bimeze kuri koronavirusi zitera ibicurane.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu baherutse kwandura cyangwa bari mu gihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro bashobora gukora virusi nyinshi mu bikorwa byabo bya buri munsi, bigatuma kurwanya icyorezo bigorana cyane.
Icyakora, SARS-CoV yari ifatwa nk'ikwirakwira iturutse ku barwayi barembye cyane, kandi nta gihamya kinini cy'uko ishobora kwandura mu cyiciro cya mbere.
Ibi bituma icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu gikomeye cyane kandi bigoye kugenzura kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
