SARS-CoV-2 yandura cyane iyo umuntu akoroye cyangwa yitsamuye, kandi ishobora no kwandura binyuze mu guhura n'ibintu byanduye.
Iyi virusi kandi yagaragaye mu busa, bityo igaragaza ko hashobora kuba hari ubundi buryo bwo kwanduzanya binyuze mu busa.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku barwayi 138 bwagaragaje ko 41% by'abarwayi bashobora kuba barwaye indwara z'indwara z'ibyorezo, harimo 17 barwaye indwara zisanzwe n'abakozi bo mu buvuzi 40.
Ni ngombwa rero gufata ingamba zo kwirinda kugira ngo abantu barinde, cyane cyane abashinzwe ubuzima, abakozi bashinzwe imibereho myiza y'abaturage, imiryango n'abo bakorana, ndetse n'umuntu wese ushobora kuba yarahuriyeho n'abarwayi cyangwa abantu banduye.
Uburyo bwa mbere bushoboka bwo kwirinda kwandura ni ukwambara udupfukamunwa; gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi n'udupfukamunwa tw'ubuhumekero twitwa N95 (1860) bifasha mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi turinda udutonyanga dushobora kwandura guturika cyangwa gusigara ku bintu bishobora kwandurira abandi.
Icyakora, udupfukamunwa twa N95 (1860) ni two gusa dutanga uburinzi ku bantu bahumeka udukoko tw'indwara tw'ibicurane tubarirwa hagati ya 10 na 80 nm, aho 5% gusa ari zo zishobora kwinjira burundu; SARS-CoV-2 isa na SARS-CoV mu bunini kuko byombi bifite uburebure bwa 85 nm.
Kubera ko utwo duce dushobora kunyura mu masike eshanu z'ubuvuzi ziteretse ku zindi, ni ngombwa ko abaganga bahura n'abarwayi bakambara udupfukamunwa twa N95 (1860s) aho kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi.
Uretse udupfukamunwa, abakozi b'ubuzima bagomba kwambara amakanzu yo kwicungira akwiriye kugira ngo barusheho kugabanya guhura n'ubwandu.
Virusi kandi zishobora kwanduza umuntu binyuze mu jisho.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yasanze yanduye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; virusi ishobora kuba yarinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu jisho kubera ubuhumekero.
Ku bw'ibyo, abakozi b'ubuzima bagomba no kwambara udupfukamunwa cyangwa indorerwamo zirinda indwara igihe bahura n'abarwayi.
Abantu bo mu duce twanduye cyangwa dushobora kwandura, barasabwa gukaraba intoki kenshi bakoresheje isabune, bakirinda abantu benshi uko bishoboka kose kandi bakirinda guhura n'abantu bashobora kwandura.
Ni byiza ko umuntu aguma kure y'abarwayi metero imwe.
Ibyo ni uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura no kwirinda ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 ari virusi nshya ku bantu, kuba ifite aho ihuriye na SARS-CoV, nk'uko byavuzwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, bigomba kuba byaratumye Ubushinwa bujya mu bihe by'ubwihebe nyuma y'icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003.
Icyakora, ku ya 19 Mutarama 2020, umuyobozi w'ikigo cyo mu mujyi wa Wuhan gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara yijeje abaturage ko virusi nshya idashobora kwandura cyane, ko idashobora kwanduzanya n'abandi bantu kandi ko kwirinda no gukumira iyi ndwara bitoroshye.
Ubwo butumwa bwatumye abantu batavuga cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyari kigiye kwitegura Umunsi Mukuru w'Igisibo, bityo amahirwe akomeye yo guhashya iki cyorezo mu mujyi wa Wuhan aragabanuka.
Ibigo by'Ubushinwa bishinzwe kurwanya indwara bigomba kubivanamo isomo kandi bikagira icyo bikora.
Urugero, ibi bigo bigomba (1) kwitonda mu itangazo ryabyo ku baturage kuko buri jambo rifite agaciro kandi rishobora kugira ingaruka ku myitwarire n'ibyemezo by'abaturage; (2) kugaragaza ubushishozi no guhangana n'amakuru adasanzwe y'ibitaro aho gutegereza raporo z'imikorere y'abaganga cyangwa inzego z'ibanze; (3) kugira ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira icyorezo mu ntangiriro aho guhumuriza abaturage; no (4) gukora imyitozo myinshi kandi ifite ireme yo gukangurira abaturage kumenya iby'indwara z'ibyorezo, ariko kandi bagakomeza gupima no kunoza uburyo abaturage bakirwanya.
