Inkomoko ya virusi ya coronavirusi ku bantu ikomoka ku nyamaswa
Icyorezo cya SARS n'icya MERS byahinduye imiterere y'ibipimo by'ubwandu bwa HCoV, bigaragaza ko ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora kwangiza cyane kandi bukaba bushobora kwica.
HCoVs nyinshi zituruka ku ducurama tudafite ubwandu.
Impamvu imwe ni uko hari abantu benshi baterwa na HCoVs.
Kumenya abarwayi bo mu matungo bifite ingaruka ku burinzi bw'indwara z'abantu.
Kwiga ku mikoranire ya CoV n'umurwayi mu nyamaswa bishobora no gutuma abantu barushaho gusobanukirwa CoV.
Bitewe n'itandukaniro riri mu miterere ya poroteyine, CoVs zigizwe n'imiryango ine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV). Umuryango wa Beta-CoV urimo HCoVs nyinshi kandi ugabanyijemo imiryango ine (A, B, C na D).
Ibihamya bya phylogenetic byerekana ko udukoko n'imbeba ari byo bitanga amakuru y'imiterere y'indwara nyinshi za alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga amakuru menshi ya gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana abantu barindwi banduye virusi itera SIDA (HCoV).
Muri izo, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni alpha-CoVs.
Ibindi BETA-CoV eshanu ni HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
Gukurikirana inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV bitanga urufatiro rwo gusobanukirwa amateka kamere, imbaraga zituma habaho no guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'ubwoko.
Nanone kandi, ishobora kuyobora cyangwa koroshya ubushakashatsi ku muntu (abantu) urinda, uhuza n'uwufasha SARS-CoV-2, bigira ingaruka zikomeye mu kwirinda ubwandu bw'igihe kizaza.
CoV z'inyamaswa zamenyekanye kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1930.
Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, HCoV ndwi zaramenyekanye.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E bwabonetse mu nzira y'ubuhumekero y'abarwayi barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo hejuru mu 1966, nyuma buhinduka bukura mu bwoko bw'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu bihaha bwitwa WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'ibicurane bisanzwe, birimo umutwe, kwitsamura, kubabara mu muhogo no kudahumeka, umuriro n'inkorora byagaragaraga mu bantu bari hagati ya 10 na 20%.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi biboneka ku isi hose kandi bigaragara ko byandura cyane mu gihe cy'itumba, mu bihugu bifite ikirere gitoshye.
