Mu rwego rwo gukomeza kugabanya ubukene, Coles yategetse ibicuruzwa byinshi cyane ku bakiriya kandi yongera umubare w'ibyo batanga, Woolworths yategetse ibindi bicuruzwa, naho ALDI itangira gutanga ibicuruzwa hakiri kare ku wa gatatu.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa, ariko ko amategeko y'akarere ku masaha yo gutanga ibicuruzwa mu modoka atuma ibyo bigoye.
Iteganya ko ibiciro by'umusaruro bizamuka, mu gihe abaguzi bazaba bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo, kandi n'ibikorwa byo kwamamaza bigabanuke.
Ku wa kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko nyuma yo gufungura ibicuruzwa hakiri kare, amaduka amwe n'amwe adashobora kubahiriza gahunda yo ku wa gatatu.
Mu nkuru yasohotse ku rubuga rwa News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu by'ubucuruzi muri kaminuza y'ikoranabuhanga ya Queensland, yavuze ko amaduka ashyiramo ibicuruzwa buri joro.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'isuku ari ikintu kinini, bigatuma haboneka ibicuruzwa bike, iyo bimaze kubura, bigasiga ahantu henshi hatagira icyo bihingamo, bigatuma abantu bumva ko hari ibiciro bike.
 Coles na Woolworths batekereza ko niba amaduka yuzuye, niba ibicuruzwa nk'impapuro z'isuku n'imiti yica udukoko bishobora kugurwa kandi biboneka ku bwinshi, bishobora kugabanya ubwoba , Russell Zimmerman yabwiye ABC News.
Uruganda rukora impapuro z'isuku zisubiwemo rwitwa Who Gives a Crap rwatangaje ko rurangije ku isoko ku wa gatatu ushize.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora impapuro z'isuku za Kleenex, na Solaris Paper ikora impapuro za Sorbent, bavuze ko bakora amasaha 24 n'amasaha 7 kugira ngo bakomeze kubona ibikoresho, nk'uko bivugwa n'ikinyamakuru News.com.au.
Urubuga rw'imicungire y'imitungo ruzwi nka Domain.com rwatangaje ko hari abagurisha imitungo batanga impapuro z'isuku ku buntu ku muntu wa mbere uzinjiza mu cyamunara i Melbourne, mu gihe cyamunara zari nke kubera ko abaguzi bari mu kiruhuko mu mpera z'icyumweru kirekire cy'umunsi w'umurimo.
Ku wa Kane, ikinyamakuru cya NT News, cyandikwaga buri munsi mu mujyi wa Darwin, cyanditseho impapuro umunani z'inyandiko z'inyandiko zigenewe gukata zikakoreshwa nk'impapuro z'isuku.
Mu mizo ya mbere, amaduka ntiyari ashishikajwe no gushyiraho amategeko agenga ibyo kugura, nk'uko byavuzwe na ABC Australia ku ya 3 Werurwe, aho yatangaje ko nta gahunda yo gushyiraho amategeko agenga ibyo kugura yari ihari.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko hari ibindi bikoresho byari bikenewe cyane, birimo udupfukamunwa, imiti yica udukoko, ibyokurya bikama, ibikoresho by'isuku y'intoki n'ifu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Ositaraliya, ku Cyumweru nijoro, hari isoko rikomeye ryo mu Bwongereza rifite imbuga za interineti rya Ocado ryagaragaje ko kugura impapuro z'isuku za Andres byari bigabanyijemo amapaki abiri y'ibikoresho 12.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryita COVID-19 icyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryise icyorezo cya COVID-19 (indwara iterwa na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2) icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo  icyorezo  ryerekeza gusa ku rugero rw'ikwirakwira ry'indwara, aho kwerekeza ku kaga k'ubwandu bwihariye, OMS yavuze ko hakenewe ko za guverinoma zifata ingamba:
 Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyorezo.
Niba ibihugu byashakisha, bikagerageza, bikita ku bantu, bikabashyira mu kato, bikabashyira mu bikorwa kandi bikabishyira hamwe mu rwego rwo guhangana , Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, yavuze.
 Dufite impungenge zikomeye, si gusa ku bijyanye n'ubukana n'ubukana bw'iki cyorezo, ahubwo no ku bijyanye n'ubushobozi bwo kucyirinda. 
Dr Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo  kitigeze kibaho mbere .
Mu magambo yatangajwe na CNN muri Gashyantare, yavuze ko uretse ibicurane, nta zindi virusi zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero zigeze zigaragara kuva zatangira kugeza ubwo zikomeje gukwirakwira ku isi hose.
Ghebreyesus na we yagize icyo avuga kuri iki kibazo, avuga ko  tutari bwigere tubona icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus. 
Yongeyeho ati:  kandi nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe. 
Icyorezo gishya cyatewe n'icyemezo cy'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) cyo gutangaza icyorezo nk'icy'ingorane y'ubuvuzi mpuzamahanga muri Mutarama.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cya Amerika gishinzwe Indwara z'Ibitera n'Indwara Zandura, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ku cyorezo: "Mu magambo make, ibintu bizagenda birushaho kuba bibi".
Ku wa Kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko ku isi hose hari nibura abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19, hapfa abantu basaga 4600.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20 ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya Coronavirus cyatangiye mu 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye ya Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyagaragaye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Kuboza 2019, gitangazwa nk'icyorezo ku isi ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama 2020 kandi gitangazwa nk'icyorezo ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1,61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bahitana abagera ku 97.000.
Abantu bagera hafi ku 364.000 bakize.
Umubare w'abapfa ugereranywa na 4% mu Bushinwa, mu gihe mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi ugera kuri 13,04% muri Algeria na 0,08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe birimo umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Ibibazo bishobora guterwa n'iyi ndwara harimo indwara y'ibihaha n'indwara y'ubuhumekero budafite ubushobozi.
Igihe hagati yo kwanduzwa n'ibimenyetso ni iminsi igera kuri itanu ariko gishobora kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza ku minsi 14.
Nta rukingo rw'indwara cyangwa imiti yihariye ya virusi iramenyekana.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kuvurwa ni uburyo bwo kuvura ibimenyetso no kubunganira. Ingamba zo kwirinda zisabwa zirimo gukaraba intoki, gupfuka umunwa mu gihe ukoroye, kwirinda abandi bantu, no kugenzura no gushyira mu kato abantu bakekwaho kuba banduye.
Abategetsi ku isi hose bitabiriye ibi bikorwa bashyiraho amategeko abuza abantu kugenda, bashyiraho abantu mu kato, amategeko yo gutaha bataragera mu rugo, kugenzura ibyago ku kazi no gufunga ibigo.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu bukungu n'imibereho myiza ku isi hose, ibikorwa by'imikino, iby'idini, ibya politiki n'umuco birasubikwa cyangwa birahagarikwa, kandi hari ubukene bw'ibiribwa bwongerewe bitewe no kugura ibintu mu buryo butunguranye.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe mu bihugu 193 no mu nzego z'ibanze, bigira ingaruka ku banyeshuri bagera kuri 99,4% ku isi.
Amakuru y'ibinyoma kuri virusi yakwirakwijwe kuri interineti, kandi habayeho ibikorwa by'ivangura n'ivangura ku Bashinwa, abandi bantu bakomoka mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'uburasirazuba bwa Aziya n'abo mu bindi bihugu, ndetse n'abandi baturutse mu duce dufite ubwandu bwinshi bwa virusi.
Kubera kugabanuka kw'ingendo no gufunga inganda zikomeye, habayeho kugabanuka kw'ibyuka bihumanya ikirere no kugabanuka kw'umwuka wa karubone.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) batangaje ko ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 havutse umuntu umwe wanduye indwara y'ibihaha itera indwara zitazwi, maze hatangira iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abenshi mu banduye bafatiwe mu isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, bityo bikekwa ko iyi virusi ishobora kuba yaturutse ku nyamaswa.
Virusi yateje iki cyorezo yitwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi iherutse kuvumburwa ifitanye isano ya bugufi na koronavirusi y'ikiburindi, koronavirusi y'inguge na SARS-CoV. Nyuma yaho, byaje kugaragara ko umuntu wa mbere wari ufite ibimenyetso yari yarwaye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi ko nta sano bigaragara yari afitanye n'aho isoko ry'ibiribwa bihiye ryatangiriye.
Mu bantu ba mbere banditswe mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019, bibiri bya gatatu byabonetse ko bafitanye isano n'isoko.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, ikinyamakuru South China Morning Post cyatangaje ko umuntu wa mbere wanduye ashobora kuba ari uwa 17 Ugushyingo 2019, akaba yari afite imyaka 55 y'amavuko wo mu ntara ya Hubei. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko kubera ko abanduye bashya bagaragaye bagabanuka mu Bushinwa ariko bakongera mu buryo butunguranye mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, umubare w'abanduye bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze umubare w'abanduye bashya mu Bushinwa ku nshuro ya mbere.
Hashobora kuba hari umubare muto w'abarwayi, cyane cyane abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Ku ya 26 Gashyantare, hari abantu bake cyane banduye mu rubyiruko, kuko abari munsi y'imyaka 19 bari 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Umujyanama mukuru mu bya siyansi mu Bwongereza, Patrick Vallance, yavuze ko 60% by'abatuye u Bwongereza bagomba kwandura mbere y'uko ubwirinzi bw'ingurube bukora.
Umubare w'abanduye ni umubare w'abantu bapimwe bagasanga bafite COVID-19, kandi bagasanga basanze bafite virusi itera COVID-19 hakurikijwe amabwiriza yemewe.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyigeze kigerageza abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi ibihugu byinshi byari bifite politiki yo kudapima abantu bagaragaza ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye n'u Busuwisi.
Ubushakashatsi bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, 86% by'abanduye COVID-19 batari barigeze bamenyekana, kandi ko 79% by'abanduye bagaragaye ari abanduye bitewe n'ubwandu butanditse.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani warutaga kure cyane umubare w'abamaze kwandura.
Ibipimo bya mbere by'ibanze by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 (R0) byari hagati ya 1,4 na 2,4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara bwagaragaje ko ishobora kuba 5.7.
Abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 barakira.
Ku barwayi batavura, igihe kuva ibimenyetso bitangira kugeza bapfuye kiri hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, akenshi ni iminsi 14.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97.000 bari bamaze gupfa bazize COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, ku ya 5 Gashyantare, abagera kuri 80% by'abapfuye bari bafite imyaka 60 n'abayirengeje, naho 75% bari barwaye indwara zisanzwe nk'indwara z'umutima n'iz'umutima na diyabete. Imibare y'abantu bapfuye bishwe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri rusange yerekeza ku bapfuye basanzwemo COVID hakurikijwe amabwiriza yemewe.
Umubare w'abapfuye by'ukuri ba COVID-19 ushobora kuba uri hejuru cyane, kuko ushobora kuba utarimo abapfuye batapimwe - urugero nko mu ngo, mu bigo byita ku bageze mu za bukuru n'ahandi.
Amakuru amwe n'amwe aturuka mu Butaliyani agaragaza ko umubare w'abapfa benshi muri iki cyorezo ukubye incuro 4-5 umubare w'abapfuye bishwe na COVID.
Umuvugizi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara (CDC) yemeye ko  tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye watangajwe] utavugwaho byinshi , ibyo bikaba byemezwa n'amakuru y'ibyamamare avuga ko muri Amerika abantu batavuzwe cyane. Uko kutabamenyesha ibintu cyane biba mu gihe cy'ibyorezo, urugero nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cya H1N1 mu 2009. Umuntu wa mbere wapfuye yemejwe ni uwaturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020.
Umuntu wa mbere wapfuye hanze y'Ubushinwa bwagaragaye ku ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho uwa mbere wapfuye hanze ya Aziya agaragazwa mu Bufaransa ku ya 14 Gashyantare.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'u Bushinwa, abantu barenga 12 bapfuye mu bihugu bitandukanye ni Iran, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu n'uturere birenga mirongo ine byari byatangaje ko abantu bapfuye, ku migabane yose uretse Antarctica. Hari ibipimo byinshi bikoreshwa mu gupima umubare w'abapfa.
Iyi mibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi biganishwa n'umubare w'ibipimo, ubuziranenge bw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe cy'icyorezo, hamwe n'ibiranga abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina, ariko cyane cyane ubuzima. Umubare w'abapfa ugereranya umubare w'abapfuye ugabanyijwemo umubare w'abanduye mu gihe runaka.
Imibare ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins igaragaza ko ku isi yose, imibare y'abapfa ku isi yose ari 6.0% (97 039/1 617 204) kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare uratandukanye bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'abandura n'abapfa yagabanutse iva kuri 17,3% (ku bagaragaje ibimenyetso hagati ya tariki ya 1 na 10 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0,7% (ku bagaragaje ibimenyetso nyuma ya tariki ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ibindi bipimo ni igipimo cy'abapfa (ibipimo by'abapfa), ni ukuvuga umubare w'abanduye bapfa bishwe n'indwara, n'icy'abanduye (ibipimo by'abanduye), ni ukuvuga umubare w'abanduye (bafite ibimenyetso n'abatarabifite) bapfa bishwe n'indwara.
Iyi mibare ntabwo ihagarariye igihe kandi ikurikirana abaturage runaka kuva ku banduye kugeza ku ndwara irangiye.
Abahanga mu bya siyansi benshi bagerageje kubara iyo mibare ku bantu runaka.
Ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oxford gishinzwe ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso, gitekereza ko ubwandu bw'icyorezo muri rusange buri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Igiciro kiri hejuru muri iki cyiciro gihuje n'ibyavuye mu bipimo bya mbere bya COVID-19 byakozwe mu buryo butunguranye mu Budage, n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bugaragaza ingaruka z'ibizamini ku bipimo by'ubwandu.
OMS ivuga ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cy'ikirenga cy'icyorezo n'igihe kizamara ntibiramenyekana kandi bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya Leta ya Pennsylvania yagize ati:  Iyo nta gukumira, ubusanzwe indwara zandura zigenda zigenda zisubira inyuma, nyuma zigatangira kugabanuka igihe indwara iba itakiboneka.
Ariko ubu, biragoye cyane kumenya igihe ibyo bizabera.
Umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi wa guverinoma y'Ubushinwa, Zhong Nanshan, yavuze ko  ibi bishobora kurangira muri Kamena  mu gihe ibihugu byose byashyira hamwe bikurikiza inama zatanzwe na OMS ku ngamba zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu Ishuri ry'isuku n'ubuvuzi bw'ikirere ry'i Londres yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2  izakomeza gukwirakwira, wenda mu gihe cy'umwaka cyangwa ibiri .
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson wo muri Imperial College bwagaragaje ko abantu bagomba kwitandukanya n'abandi kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse (mu mezi 18 cyangwa arenga).
William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati: "Ntekereza ko coronavirus idashobora guhita ishira burundu kuko yandura mu buryo bworoshye, kandi ishobora guhinduka indwara y'igihe, ishobora kugaruka buri mwaka".
Uburemere bw'ubu bushya buza bushingiye ku bushobozi bw'ingurube n'ubunini bw'ihinduka ry'imiterere.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 hari igihe biba bidasanzwe, kandi abantu bayanduye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro (88%) n'inkorora yumye (68%).
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara ni umunaniro, guhumeka ibintu by'umwuka (mucous), kubura impumuro, guhumeka nabi, ububabare mu ngingo n'imitsi, kubabara mu muhogo, umutwe, kugira ubwoba, gusubiranamo, kuvira amaraso, iseseme cyangwa kurwara ibicurane. OMS ivuga ko umuntu umwe kuri batandatu arwaye cyane kandi afite ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) kivuga ibimenyetso byihutirwa nk'ububabare bwo guhumeka, kubabara cyangwa guhinda umushyitsi mu gatuza, guhinda umushyitsi, kubyuka bigoye, n'ubururu bw'amaso cyangwa iminwa; iyo ibimenyetso bihari, bisaba ko umuntu ahita afashwa. Iyo indwara ikomeje gukomera ishobora gutera amapfunwe akomeye, indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, kuvira amaraso mu maraso, guhindagurika kw'amaraso no gupfa.
Bamwe mu banduye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso, nta bimenyetso by'uburwayi bagaragaza ariko ibipimo byabemeje ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi batanze inama ko abantu bahuye n'abanduye bagombye gukurikiranwa no gusuzumwa kugira ngo hatagira ubandura.
Ibipimo by'Ubushinwa ku kigero cy'abadafite ibimenyetso bya virusi biri hagati ya 44% na 44%.
Igihe gisanzwe cyo kuboneza urubyaro (igihe kuva umuntu yanduye kugeza agaragaje ibimenyetso) kiri hagati y'umunsi umwe na 14; akenshi ni iminsi itanu. Urugero rwiza rw'ukutabona neza, ni uko imibare y'abantu bafite COVID-19 batumva impumuro yari 30% mbere y'uko igera kuri 15%.
Hari amakuru menshi ku buryo iyi ndwara ikwirakwira ataraboneka.
Bivugwa ko iyi ndwara yandura cyane cyane mu gihe umuntu afitanye isano ya hafi n'undi, binyuze mu gutonyanga utuntu duto cyane mu gihe ari gukorora, kwitsamura cyangwa kuvuga; iyo mishyikirano ya hafi iba hagati ya metero 1 na 2.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukorora udakoresheje umwambaro ushobora gutera ibitonyanga mu maso biri hagati ya metero 15 na metero 8.2.
Hari abavuze ko virusi ishobora no kwandura binyuze mu matembabuzi mato cyane aguma mu mwuka igihe kirekire, ashobora guturuka mu mvugo. Matembabuzi yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ashobora no guturuka mu gihe umuntu ahumetse, cyane cyane mu mvugo, nubwo ubusanzwe virusi idaterwa n'ikirere.
Ibipimo bishobora kugera mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abandi bantu bari iruhande cyangwa se bikanahumwa mu bihaha.
Hari uburyo bwo kuvura nk'imashini yo gutera mu nda no guhuha (CPR) bushobora gutuma umuntu ahumeka ibintu byinshi, bityo bikamwirakwiza mu kirere.
Nanone ishobora gukwirakwira iyo umuntu akoze ku kintu cyanduye, urugero nk'uruhu, mbere yo gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa akanwa.
Nubwo hari abatinya ko ishobora kwandura binyuze mu musarani, iki kibazo gifatwa nk'icyoroshye.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 idashobora kwandura binyuze mu busa. Virusi yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, ariko ikwirakwira mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara no mu gihe indwara imaze igihe kirekire.
Abantu basuzumwe bagasanga barwaye mbere y'iminsi itatu ibimenyetso bitangiye, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko hashobora kubaho ubwandu mbere y'uko ibimenyetso by'ingenzi bitangira kugaragara.
Hari raporo nke z'abanduye batagaragaza ibimenyetso byemejwe na laboratwari, ariko mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe, abantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bagaragaye mu gihe cyo gushakisha abo bahuye.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo bitaramenyekana neza uko ubwandu bwandura, ubusanzwe umuntu umwe yandurira abandi bantu babiri cyangwa batatu.
Mu by'ukuri, virusi yashoboraga kugaragara nyuma y'iminsi itatu kuri plastiki (polypropylene) na 304 z'ibyuma bitagira ingeso, nyuma y'umunsi umwe kuri karito, na nyuma y'amasaha ane kuri umuringa.
Ariko kandi, biterwa n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe. Amatungo yo mu ngo n'andi matungo yasanganywe COVID-19.
Nta gihamya igaragaza ko inyamaswa zishobora kwanduza abantu, ariko abategetsi bo mu Bwongereza batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, nko gukorana n'ibindi bintu bishobora kuba byakozwe n'abantu banduye.
Indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye ya 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ni virusi nshya, yabanje gutandukanywa n'abantu batatu barwaye ibicurane by'ibihaha bifitanye isano n'icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero i Wuhan.
Ibintu byose biranga virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 biboneka muri koronavirusi zihuriye mu bidukikije. Iyo virusi idakoreshejwe mu mubiri w'umuntu, iseswa n'isabune yo mu rugo, ikamenagura igifu cyayo. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya bugufi na SARS-CoV ya mbere.
Bemeza ko byaturutse ku bikoko.
