Taiwan yongereye ibicuruzwa by'udupfukamunwa kandi ihagarika ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi. Imyitozo yo mu Bwongereza na Amerika igaragaza ko kugabanya (kugabanya ariko kudahita bihagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kugihagarika (kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) bigoranye cyane.
Politiki nziza yo kugabanya ubwandu ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abahakwa kwitabwaho n'ubuzima ku kigero cya 2/3 n'abapfa ku kigero cya kimwe cya kabiri, ariko ntibishobora kwirinda urupfu rw'abantu ibihumbi amagana, kandi inzego z'ubuzima zirarengewe.
Gukumira bishobora kuba byiza, ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ari rwo rwabanje kubaho), kuko bitabaye ibyo, ikwirakwira ryongera kwihuta iyo ingamba zigabanyijwe.
Gushyiraho ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhashya iki cyorezo bifite ikiguzi cy'imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta miti ya virusi yemewe yo kuvura COVID-19, ariko hari ibikorwa byo kuyikora birimo no kugerageza imiti iriho.
Kunywa imiti ya frigo cyangwa kunywa ibinyobwa hamwe no kuruhuka bishobora gufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere, imiti ya ogisijeni, guterwa intanga n'ubufasha mu guhumeka bishobora kuba ngombwa.
Gukoresha steroid bishobora gutuma ibisubizo birushaho kuba bibi.
Imiti myinshi yari yemewe mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi ubu iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi mu kuvura COVID-19.
