ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere by'u Burayi bya OMS byasohoye amabwiriza yo kwita ku bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ku bijyanye no kongera gushyira imbaraga mu nzego zitandukanye, harimo gushyira serivisi za laboratwari mu gupima COVID-19, guhagarika ibikorwa bitari ngombwa aho bishoboka, gutandukanya no gushyira mu kato abarwayi basanganywe COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi bababaye cyane binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'imashini zitanga umwuka n'ibitanda.
