Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yakwirakwiriye mu zindi ntara zo mu Bushinwa, ifashwa n'impunzi zo mu gihe cy'Ubunani no kuba Wuhan ari ihuriro ry'ingendo ndetse n'aho gari ya moshi zihurira.
