Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 byagize nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije ingendo kandi bishyiraho igenzura ku mipaka.
Ibisubizo by'igihugu byose birimo ingamba zo kwirinda nk'igenzurwa ry'abantu (zwi no ku izina ry'amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo, kuguma mu nzu cyangwa gufunga abantu) n'amabwiriza yo gutaha batemerewe. Kugeza ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90 ku ijana by'abatuye Amerika, bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga abantu, abantu barenga miriyoni 50 bari muri Filipine, abagera kuri miriyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo na miriyari 1,3 mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1,7 ku isi bari bafite uburyo runaka bwo kwirinda, nyuma y'iminsi ibiri uwo mubare wariyongereye ugera kuri miliyari 2.6 - hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 yavumbuwe ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo itemejwe igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wemejwe yanduye yavumbuwe ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Ku ya 26 Ukuboza, umuganga Zhang Jixian yabonye ko hari abantu benshi barwaye indwara y'ibihaha itagira icyorezo, maze ku ya 27 Ukuboza, abimenyesha ikigo cya Wuhan Jianghan CDC.
Ibizamini bya mbere byagenewe ibipimo by'abarwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byagaragaje ko coronavirus isa na SARS.
Itangazo ry'abaturage ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza.
WHO yabimenyeshejwe uwo munsi.
Abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bahawe umuburo kubera ko  bakwirakwije ibihuha  ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta gihamya kigaragara cyo kwandura hagati y'abantu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukabije, nyuma buvugwa n'Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping ko ari "intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Mu cyiswe "igikorwa gikomeye cyo gushyira abantu mu kato" mu mateka y'isi, ku ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe itegeko ryo guhagarika ingendo ziva n'izigera i Wuhan, ryongerewe rigera ku mijyi 15 yo mu ntara ya Hubei, rigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byarabujijwe mu mujyi.
Iminsi mikuru y'Ubunani (ya 25 Mutarama) yahagaritswe mu duce twinshi.
Abategetsi kandi batangaje ko bagiye kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, Huoshenshan, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hubatswe indi bitaro: Leishenshan, kugira ngo havurwe abarwayi benshi.
Uretse ibyo bitaro bishya, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 byo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, urugero nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro na za sitade, bihinduka ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga raporo z'ubuzima ku bagenzi no kongera iminsi mikuru y'Igisibo.
Kaminuza n'amashuri yo mu gihugu na byo byafunzwe.
Intara za Hong Kong na Macao zashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Ingamba zo gukorera kure zashyizweho mu turere dutandukanye two mu Bushinwa.
Ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo zashyizweho muri Hubei no hanze yayo.
Imodoka zitwara abantu benshi zahinduwe, kandi amazu ndangamurage yo mu Bushinwa yafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Gucunga ingendo z'abaturage byashyizwe mu mijyi myinshi, kandi bivugwa ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bari bafite uburyo runaka bwo kubuzwa kujya mu tundi duce. Nyuma y'aho icyorezo cyatangiriye ku isi hose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi yinjira mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho gahunda yo gushyira mu kato abantu bose bavuye mu bindi bihugu binjira muri uwo mujyi mu gihe cy'iminsi 14. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa bw'ibanze hari umuntu umwe gusa wanduye mu minsi itanu yabanjirije iy'icyumweru cya mbere, muri iki gihe akaba yari umuntu wari waturutse muri Istanbul agaruka i Canton.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bw'abanduye mu gihugu ryahise rihagarikwa, kandi ko icyorezo cyagenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingendo zari zibuzanyijwe muri Hubei, uretse Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri gahunda yo gufunga abantu itangiye. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira mu Bushinwa ku bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura bizasubikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko ntiyavuze igihe iyo gahunda izarangirira.
Abantu bifuza kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba visa muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsili z'Ubushinwa.
Leta y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije inganda n'inganda gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga gahunda zo gufasha inganda mu by'amafaranga. Inama y'Igihugu ishinzwe ubucuruzi yatangaje umunsi wo kurira uzatangirana no guceceka iminota itatu ku ya 4 Mata saa kumi za mu gitondo, bihuye n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo leta y'ibanze yasabye imiryango kujya mu muhango wo kwibuka ku rubuga rwa interineti kugira ngo abantu bakomeze kugirana imishyikirano hagati yabo kandi birinde ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyongera kwaduka.
Byaremejwe ko COVID-19 yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020 iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habaye ukwiyongera gukomeye kw'abanduye, ahanini biturutse ku nama yabereye i Daegu y'umuryango mushya w'idini witwa Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abitabiriye imihango yo gusengera Shincheonji bari baje i Daegu baturutse i Wuhan, bakekwaho kuba ari bo bateje iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bantu 9,336 bari mu rusengero, 1,261 cyangwa 13% bavuze ko bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko hari umuburo ukomeye ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, hanyuma ku ya 29 Gashyantare haboneka abandi 3.150.
Ibigo byose by'ingabo muri Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'aho abasirikare batatu basanganywe virusi.
Amasaha y'indege na yo yarahindutse, bityo Koreya y'Epfo yatangije gahunda yafashwe nk'iy'ingenzi kandi iteganyijwe neza ku isi yo gupima abaturage kugira ngo bamenye niba nta bwandu bafite, kandi ishyira mu kato abantu bose banduye, ikagenzura kandi igashyira mu kato abantu bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima bwagombaga kuba ari uko abantu bavuye mu bindi bihugu bagombaga gutanga ibimenyetso ku giti cyabo bakoresheje porogaramu ya telefoni, bakoresheje imashini za virusi bagatanga ibisubizo ku munsi ukurikiyeho, kandi bakongera ubushobozi bwo gupima kugira ngo buri munsi abantu bagera hafi ku 20.000 bapimwe.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'aho yagize icyo igeraho mu kurwanya icyorezo, nubwo itashyize mu kato imigi yose. Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari batandukanye ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yakiriye icyo kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon ashinjwa kuba yarakoresheje nabi iki cyorezo cyangwa se bashima uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yabonye umubare muto w'abandura ku munsi mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bavuye mu mahanga bazajya mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Amakuru atangwa n'ibitangazamakuru avuga ko ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ibyifuzo by'ibihugu 121 byo kuyisaba ubufasha mu gupima virusi.
Irani yatangaje ko abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi mu by'Ubuvuzi yavuze ko abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma yaho kuri uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, siporo n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga za kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyize mu bikorwa miliyari eshanu z'amadolari y'Amerika yo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twugarijwe n'icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rw'abantu benshi hagati y'imijyi rwabaye mbere y'Ubunani bw'umwaka mushya w'Abaperesi.
Insengero z'Abashiya i Qom zakomeje gufungurirwa abagenzi kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020. Irani yabaye ihuriro ry'ikwirakwira rya virusi nyuma y'Ubushinwa muri Gashyantare.
Nyuma y'ibirego by'uko icyorezo cya Iran gishobora kuba cyarapfukiranwe, ibihugu birenga icumi byatangaje ko byavuye muri Iran ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha abarwayi 388 bari batangajwe na leta ya Iran kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, mu gihe 23 mu bagize 290 bayigize bavuze ko basanze basanganywe virusi ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza kurekura nta mpamvu, abaharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira kuba abatavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi mu mahoro, no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zujuje ibisabwa.
Uyu muryango wavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira kwa virusi mu bigo bifunze nk'ibigo by'ifungwa, nabyo bidafite ubuvuzi.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, ni umubare munini w'abapfuye muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba Irani bahoze cyangwa bariho n'abategetsi bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara ku ya 17 Werurwe.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yagaragaje ubwandu bushya 50 buri saha, n'urupfu rushya rw'umuntu umwe muri buri minota icumi.
Umuyobozi wa OMS yavuze ko muri Irani hashobora kuba hari abantu barwaye barenze incuro eshanu umubare w'abamaze kwandura.
Hari kandi abavuga ko ibihano bya Amerika bishobora gutuma icyo gihugu kidabasha guhangana n'iki cyorezo mu buryo bw'amafaranga.
Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye gishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu cyasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanya ibihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Byaremejwe ko iki cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa basangwaga na SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Abanduye batangiye kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse, bituma leta y'u Butaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege zijya n'izisohoka mu Bushinwa kandi itangaza ko ibintu byihutirwa.
Nyuma yaho, havumbuwe abantu 16 banduye COVID-19 batigeze bavugwaho aho baherereye, ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare mu ntara ya Lombardie. Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya rigamije gukumira icyorezo, harimo no gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50.000 bo mu turere 11 dutandukanye two mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yavuze:  Mu bice byibasiwe n'icyorezo, nta muntu wemerewe kwinjira cyangwa gusohoka.
Imirimo n'imikino byarahagaritswe muri utwo duce. Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza bifunga burundu mu gihugu, mu gihe mu Butaliyani hapfuye abantu 100.
Imikino ikomeye yose, harimo n'imikino y'umupira w'amaguru ya Serie A, yagombaga kuba mu rugo kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bihagarara, uretse amaduka manini n'amaduka y'imiti. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Sosiyete y'Ubutaliyani y'Abaganga b'Ibitera Agahinda, Abapima, Abafasha mu Buzima no mu Bundi Buvuzi bw'Ibitaro Bwihutirwa (SIAARTI) yasohoye inama ku bijyanye n'imyifatire y'abaganga ku buryo bwo gupima bushobora gukurikizwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwatsinze Ubushinwa buza ku mwanya wa mbere ku isi mu bihugu byagize umubare munini w'abahitanywe na coronavirus nyuma yo gutanga raporo y'abantu 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko u Burusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'intambara zari zifite ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, u Butaliyani bwari bufite abarwayi 128,948, abapfuye 15,887 n'abakize 21,815, abenshi muri abo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardie.
Inkuru ya CNN yavuze ko kuba mu Butaliyani abantu benshi bageze mu za bukuru kandi abantu bose banduye virusi bakaba batarapimwa kugeza ubu, bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye abantu benshi bapfa.
Igisubizo cy'Ubwongereza kuri iyi virusi cyabanje kugaragara nk'icyoroshye kurusha ibindi bihugu byazahajwe, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyari yarashyizeho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutandukanya abantu cyangwa gushyira abantu mu kato.
Ku bw'ibyo, leta yanenzwe ko idakomeye kandi ko idakora cyane mu gusubiza ibibazo by'abaturage. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje itangazo, atanga inama yo kwirinda ingendo zose zidakenewe no guhura n'abantu, asaba abantu gukorera mu ngo zabo igihe bishoboka kandi bakirinda ahantu nko mu tubari, muri resitora no mu mazu y'imyidagaduro.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro nk'amabyiniro n'amazu y'imikino bigomba gufunga vuba bishoboka, kandi yiyemeza kwishyura abakozi 80% by'umushahara, ku gipimo cya £2,500 ku kwezi, mu rwego rwo kwirinda ubushomeri buterwa n'ikibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda abantu, abuza abantu guteranira hamwe barenze babiri kandi agabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze mu gihe ari ngombwa.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'uko byari bimeze mbere, izo ngamba zari zifite ibihano bya polisi, harimo gucibwa amande no gusenya amateraniro.
Ibigo byinshi by'ubucuruzi byategetswe gufunga uretse ibifatwa nk'ibikenewe cyane, birimo amaduka manini, farumasi, banki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ubwoko bwose, za gari ya moshi n'amategura.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wari ufite COVID-19 yemejwe mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika, muri leta ya Washington, ku mugabo wari waturutse i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'ibanze ry'ibiro bya White House rishinzwe kurwanya coronavirus ryatangijwe ku ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ubuzima bw'abaturage bwihutirwa kandi bushyiraho amategeko abuza abagenzi kuva mu Bushinwa kwinjira.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, ikigo cy'ubuzima rusange cya mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho byacyo byo gupima.
Nubwo byari bimeze bityo ariko, Amerika yatinze gutangira gupima, bituma abantu batamenya uko icyo cyorezo cyari giteye icyo gihe.
Ibizamini byatewe n'ibikoresho byo gupima bidakora neza byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, leta ntiyemera ibikoresho byo gupima bitari ibya leta (amashuri makuru, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, kandi hari ingingo zifatika zo gusaba gupimwa kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (nyuma y'aho itegeko ry'umuganga ryari ngombwa).
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru The Washington Post cyatangaje ko ibizamini byafashwe muri Amerika bigeze munsi ya 4.000.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hasigaye ibipimo 14 000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru Associated Press cyatangaje ko:  Abantu benshi bagaragaza ibimenyetso kandi bagasaba abaganga kubisuzuma bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi kugira ngo bapimwe. Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika rwatangajwe muri leta ya Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko habaye ibyago, ibindi bihugu na byo bibikurikiza vuba.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi hagati muri Werurwe amashuri yo hirya no hino mu gihugu yari afunze. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'ibyorezo bo muri Imperial College London bamenyesheje Amerika ingaruka zitezwe z'icyorezo cya coronavirus gishya ku gihugu.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ry'inyongera ry'ingengo y'imari yo kwitegura no guhangana na Coronavirus, ritanga inkunga y'ingoboka ya miliyari 8,3 z'amadolari yo gufasha inzego za leta guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yahagaritse abakozi bayo gukora ingendo, yahagaritse inama kandi ashishikariza abakozi gukora bari mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibihe by'umwaka byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari ingendo zibujijwe mu Burayi hafi ya bwose, usibye mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30 guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, yaguyeho amategeko agenga ingendo mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu, bituma haboneka amafaranga ya leta yo guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi byafunze cyangwa bigabanya amasaha yabyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika mu rwego rwo kugerageza gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe muri buri gihugu muri leta 50 n'Akarere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, abantu 10.700 barwaye coronavirus muri New York, baruta umubare w'abanduye bose muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda abantu bigaragara ko ari byiza kuko imibare y'abanduye yavuye ku minsi 2.0 igera ku minsi 4.7.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe, muri New York hari hamaze kumenyekana abantu 32 308 banduye iyi virusi, naho abantu 672 barayipfushije. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yatangaje abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku ya 8 Mata, muri Amerika hari hamaze kumenyekana abantu 400 335 banduye iyi virusi, naho abantu 12 841 barayipfushije.
Ku ya 30 Werurwe, binyuze mu itangazamakuru, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort, bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1000, bwageze i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Amerika yatangaje ko abantu 884 bishwe na coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Muri Leta ya New York, umubare w'abanduye warenze 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. Ibiro bya Perezida byanenzwe ko byagabanyije akaga kandi bikagenzura itumanaho, bigategeka abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza itangazo rusange n'ibitabo bijyanye na virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Kwemera muri rusange uburyo Trump yakemuye iki kibazo byateje amacakubiri mu mashyaka.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze ko Amerika ishingiye ku bushobozi bwo kwinjiza ibikoresho by'ingenzi cyane cyane ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ingenzi, bivuye mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'ingendo z'indege ryakoreshejwe mu kwerekana no guhanura uburyo ikwirakwira, kandi ryashyizwe mu kinyamakuru Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere hagati kwa 2020.
Amakuru yo mu 2018 y'ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga ry'ingendo z'indege avuga ko Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ari byo bihugu byagize umubare munini w'abagenzi bavuye i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byari ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abantu bavaga i Wuhan.
Bali yafashwe nk'umugi wa mbere udakora neza mu mijyi 20 ikunzwe cyane ihagera mu kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yafashwe nk'aho ikora neza kurushaho. Ositaraliya yashyize ahagaragara gahunda yayo y'ubutabazi bwihuta bwa Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku ya 7 Gashyantare.
Yavuze ko hakiri byinshi byo kumenya kuri COVID-19 kandi ko Australia izongera kugenzura imipaka no gutangaza amakuru mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habayeho ikibazo cy'umutekano muke mu buzima bw'abantu.
Kubera ko imodoka zitwara abantu n'ibintu z'i Wuhan na Hubei zashyizwe mu kato, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gutahukana abaturage n'abakozi ba za dipolomasi muri ako karere, ahanini hakoreshejwe indege zitangirwa n'igihugu cy'iwabo, babifashijwemo n'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Australia, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byateguye guhungisha abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yatangaje ko itazavana abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yavanye muri icyo gihugu Abaturage 34 b'Abanyabrezili cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, hamwe n'Abanyapolonye bane, Umushina n'Umuhinde.
Abaturage ba Pologne, Ubushinwa n'Ubuhinde bageze muri Pologne, aho indege ya Bresil yahagaze mbere yo gukomeza urugendo yerekeza muri Bresil.
Abaturage ba Burezili bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanaada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere na 39 bari mu yindi yari ikodeshejwe na Leta ya Amerika) bakuwe i Wuhan bajya muri BFC Trenton kugira ngo bashyirwe mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 ivuye i Wuhan yageze kuri BFC Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Ositaraliya bakuye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare mu kigo cyo gufungira ku kirwa cya Christmas, cyabaye ikigo cy'abashyirwa mu kato, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Indege y'i Nouvelle-Zélande yageze i Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo n'abaturutse muri Ositaraliya no mu karere ka Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cy'ingabo z'igihugu cya Whangaparaoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye kuvana Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bakuwe mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye gucyura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari ikodeshejwe na guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yasubije muri Afurika y'Epfo abaturage 112.
Abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus bagumye aho kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago byo kwandura.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo gusa bagaragayeho ko nta bwandu bafite ni bo basubijwe mu gihugu.
Ibisubizo by'ibizamini byakuyeho ibyaha abaturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bose bari mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri Ranch Resort kubera kwirinda.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa biga muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bateraniye hamwe kugira ngo bafashe kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byibasiwe n'iyi virusi, hamwe n'itsinda rihuriweho ryo mu karere ka Chicago rivuga ko ryohereje udupfukamunwa 50 000 twa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango wita ku butabazi Direct Relief, ufatanyije na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa 200 000 n'ibindi bikoresho birinda umuntu, harimo n'amaboko n'imyenda, binyuze mu ndege y'ubutabazi bw'agateganyo ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya Amerika ku kigo cy'isi cyita ku buzima (OMS) kugira ngo bashyigikire ubushakashatsi ku rukingo, mu bikorwa byo kuruvura no kurinda  abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo .
Interaksiyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge y'i Singapour yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga y'amadolari y'Amerika agera kuri miliyoni 2.26 mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa tw'ubwirinzi miliyoni 1 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya bwoherereje Wuhan toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Maleziya yatangaje ko izatangaza uturindantoki tw'ubuvuzi miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo udupfukamunwa 10,000 twa Hazmat, Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi isezeranya ibindi bihugu byazahajwe na coronavirus inkunga y'amafaranga angana na miliyoni 100 z'amadolari. Uko ubwandu bw'abanduye muri Ubushinwa bwagendaga bugabanuka, icyo gihugu cyatangiye kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byinshi byatewe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'u Burusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1 by'imiti, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda abantu i Addis Abeba muri Ethiopia kugira ngo itangirwe n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho yoherereje Panama ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho 5 byo guhumeka.
Ma kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Kanada. U Buholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque bagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye n'udupfukamunwa n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye mu Bushinwa ibikoresho 58,000 byo gupima coronavirus byakozwe mu Bushinwa bifite 30% gusa by'ukuri, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwo bwongeye kwibutsa Ubushinwa udupfukamunwa 600,000 dufite inenge.
Ububiligi bwasubije mu bikorwa udupfukamunwa 100,000 tudakoreshwa, twatekerejwe ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza mu bice bya Amerika y'Amajyepfo na Afurika. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubufasha bw'imvura n'izuba ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimiye abayobozi b'Ubushinwa ku bw'imihati bashyizeho mu gucunga no gukumira iki cyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga guhisha ko byateye inzitizi mu bikorwa byo kwirinda no gukumira, n'ikibazo kiriho ubu aho leta nkuru  yatanze raporo zisanzwe mu kwirinda ubwoba mu ijoro ryabanjirije Umwaka Mushya w'ukwezi .
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ibanze cyo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Gauden Galea, uhagarariye OMS yavuze ko nubwo atari inama y'OMS, ariko ko ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cy'uko twiyemeje guhashya icyorezo aho cyagwiriye cyane, kandi avuga ko ari ikintu kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange. Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko mu Bushinwa hari ubwandu bw'abantu n'ubw'abantu kandi umubare w'abanduye ukomeza kwiyongera mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima rusange ku rwego mpuzamahanga (USPPI), kikaba ari icya gatandatu kivugwa kuva icyorezo cya grippe cyatangira mu 2009.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko USPPI iterwa n'ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abifite amikoro yo hagati bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
Mu gusubiza ku ihagarikwa ry'ingendo, Tedros yagize ati:  nta mpamvu n'imwe yatuma ingamba zibuza ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga  kandi  OMS ntidusaba ko ingendo n'ubucuruzi bibuzwa .
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira gahunda yo kwitegura mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, ivuga ko byihutirwa gufasha ibyo bihugu  bidafite uburyo bwo gutahura abantu banduye virusi, nubwo ishobora kuba iri hafi kugaragara .
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko  dukomeye nk'urugo rwacu rw'intoki rukomeye cyane , asaba amahanga yose  gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura byinshi ejo . Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru ko iki cyorezo ari COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni António Guterres yemeye gushyira imbaraga z'umuryango w'abibumbye mu bisubizo.
Iki kigo cy'umuryango w'abibumbye kivuga ko iki gikorwa kizatuma abakozi b'ibigo by'ubuvuzi  bibanda ku bikorwa byo guhangana n'iki cyorezo, mu gihe ibindi bigo byo by'umuryango w'abibumbye bizafasha mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'iki cyorezo mu rwego rw'imibereho myiza, ubukungu n'iterambere.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abakozi ba WHO ryahise rishyirwa mu Bushinwa ryo kohereza impuguke mpuzamahanga n'iz'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima mu Bushinwa kugira ngo zifashe mu gucunga igihugu no gusuzuma  uburemere n'ubwandu bw'iki cyorezo  binyuze mu gutegura amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'ibanze z'igihugu no gukora ingendo zo gusura igihugu kugira ngo barebe  ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo guhangana n'iki cyorezo mu ntara no mu turere, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu . Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yavuze ko  isi ikwiriye gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus, ivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane kuvuga ko ari icyorezo, buri gihugu kigomba kwinjira mu cyiciro cyo kwitegura .
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abakozi bafatanyije kugira ngo basuzume uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko icyiciro cy'ibyago byo kwandura Coronavirus ku isi cyavuye kuri  hejuru  kigera kuri  hejuru cyane , kikaba ari cyo cyiciro cyo hejuru cyo kugabisha no gusuzuma ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ishinzwe guhangana n'ibiza, yatanze umuburo mu itangazo agira ati: "Ibi ni ugusubira mu buzima busanzwe ku butegetsi bwose ku isi: nimukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi mugomba guhora mwiteguye, yongeraho ko ingamba nziza zo kuyirwanya zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda ibintu bibi cyane.
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu adatuma abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza ko kizabaho bivuze ko "twemera byimazeyo ko umuntu wese ku isi ashobora kwandura iyi virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gufatwa nk'icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS  ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ubukana n'ubukana bw'iki cyorezo ndetse n'uko nta cyo ikora. OMS yanenzwe cyane kubera uburyo itwaye iki cyorezo, kuko yabonye ko kidakwiye, cyane cyane kubera ko yatinze gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima bw'abaturage kandi ko cyabaye icyorezo.
Iki kibazo cyatewe inkunga n'ibyifuzo by'abantu 733.000 byo gusaba umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom kwegura, ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke nyinshi z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu zashimangiye uburenganzira bwa buri muntu muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo guhabwa ubufasha kandi ko iyo nshingano ari iya leta.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura amikoro cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba kuba impamvu yo kurobanura itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bemeje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abo mu bwoko buto, abageze mu za bukuru, abavuye mu byabo, abatagira aho baba, abari mu bukene bukabije, imfungwa, impunzi n'andi matsinda atarasobanuwe akeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ya leta irimo kwita ku ngaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage ziterwa n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubukungu n'Ubutwererane (OECD) watangije urubuga rutanga amakuru yuzuye kandi ahuje n'igihe ku bisubizo bya politiki mu bihugu bitandukanye byo ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Hagati y'amabwiriza yo gukomeza ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi no guhangana n'ingaruka z'ibihano byo gufunga no kugabanya ingendo, urubuga rwa interineti rurimo igikoresho cya Country Policy Tracker kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bihugu byombi no gufasha isi guhangana n'ikibazo cya coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Inama y'Abaminisitiri w'u Bwongereza, Michael Gove n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili, Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, kubera uburyo yakemuye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi b'intara batari bake bo mu ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti b'u Bushinwa (CCP) bakuwe ku mirimo yabo kubera uburyo bakoreshaga mu gushyira abantu mu kato mu Burasirazuba bw'u Bushinwa, mu kugaragaza ko badashimishijwe n'uko abayobozi b'abanyapolitiki bitabiriye icyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo batekereza ko icyo gikorwa cyari kigamije kurinda Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti b'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping uburakari bw'abaturage kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi bakuru b'Ubushinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze igitekerezo cya mbere cy'uko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan bahitamo kwemera ibitekerezo by'ubupfumu bivuga ko COVID-19 yakomotse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump bwo muri Amerika bwise coronavirus  virusi y'Ubushinwa  cyangwa  virusi ya Wuhan , buvuga ko mu Bushinwa  gukumira byateye virusi ubu yabaye icyorezo ku isi hose , nyuma bamwe mu bayirwanya bavuga ko ari ivangura rishingiye ku moko kandi ko ari ukugira ngo  abantu batabona ko ubutegetsi bwe budashobora guhashya iyo ndwara .
Ikinyamakuru The Daily Beast cyabonye telegrama ya leta ya Amerika isobanura uburyo bwo gutumanaho bigaragara ko bwaturutse mu nama y'umutekano w'igihugu, aho bavuga ko ingamba zafashwe ari izi:
Dusabwe kugerageza kugeza ubutumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, cyane cyane mu nama n'abanyamakuru no kuri televiziyo. Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imbaraga Ubushinwa bukoresha mu kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byugarijwe n'iyi virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa byo kwamamaza kugira ngo bugire uruhare ku isi.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga muri EU Josep Borrell yaburiye ko hari  igice cya géopolitique gikubiyemo guharanira kugira uruhare binyuze mu mvugo no ' politiki y'ubuntu'.
Borrell yavuze kandi ko  Ubushinwa bushimangira ko butandukanye na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ari umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe .
Ubushinwa bwasabye kandi Amerika gukuraho ibihano ku bihugu bya Syria, Venezuela na Iran, ariko bugahita bwoherereza ibyo bihugu bibiri ubufasha.
Udupfukamunwa 100,000 Jack Ma yatanze muri Cuba twahagaritswe n'ibihano bya Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika kandi bashinjwa kuyobya imfashanyo zigenewe ibindi bihugu zikajya mu gihugu cyabo.
Hari kandi ibindi bibazo by'amakimbirane bifitanye isano n'imisatsi byavuzwe n'ibindi bihugu, nk'u Budage, Autriche n'Ubusuwisi, Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe ibikoresho bifata umwuka bibarirwa mu magana byari bigenewe Espagne.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi utagaragaje ubufatanye n'Ubutaliyani bwazahajwe na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, Ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko  Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwashubije mu buryo bw'amahanga.
Ibi ntabwo ari byiza ku bumwe bw'ibihugu by'i Burayi .
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kuvugana kuri telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yateguriye ingabo z'Uburusiya kohereza abaganga b'ingabo, imodoka zihariye z'ubuvuzi n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo  isoko rikomeye rya politiki  ritazwi  rivuga ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo z'Uburusiya  nta kamaro kanini cyangwa nta kamaro bifite ku Butaliyani .
Uyu mushinjacyaha yavuze ko u Burusiya buri mu bikorwa byo guhohotera  mu rwego rwa politiki no mu rwego rwa dipolomasi .
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani Luigi Di Maio bahakanye ibyo bitangazamakuru byavuze kandi bagaragaza ko bashimira.
Uburusiya kandi bwohereje indege itwara imizigo irimo ubufasha bw'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin Dmitry Peskov yavuze ko  mu gutanga ubufasha ku bakorana bo muri Amerika, [Putin] atekereza ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi bo muri Amerika bazaba bamaze kwihuta, bazaba bashobora kubibasubiza igihe bibaye ngombwa .
Ingano y'imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO  Defender 2020  iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu bya Baltique, imyitozo ikomeye ya NATO kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye, izagabanywa.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament Kate Hudson yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020:  Mu bibazo by'ubuzima rusange biriho, ntibihungabanya ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi bitabiriye iyo myitozo gusa, ahubwo binashyira mu kaga n'ubw'abaturage bo mu bihugu bikoreramo . Guverinoma ya Irani yibasiwe cyane n'iyi virusi, aho abadepite bagera kuri 20 banduye, hamwe n'abandi bantu 15 bakomeye mu bya politiki bahoze cyangwa bariho.
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa ifunguye ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, asaba ubufasha avuga ko igihugu cye cyari kigorwa no kurwanya icyorezo kubera kutagira isoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani. Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika isaba gushyiraho politiki rusange y'imibereho myiza nk'uko bimeze ku bindi bihugu bikize, harimo uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima bw'abantu bose, gahunda yo kurera abana ku isi hose, ikiruhuko cy'ababyeyi bahembwa n'amafaranga menshi yo gufasha mu kwivuza.
Abasesengura politiki biteze ko ibyo bizagira ingaruka mbi ku buryo Donald Trump azongera gutorwa mu matora ya Perezida yo mu 2020. Imishyikirano ya dipolomasi hagati y'Ubuyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yaragabanutse kubera icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze  imihati y'Ubuyapani yo gushyira abantu mu kato idafite ishingiro kandi idafite icyo ivuze  nyuma y'aho Ubuyapani butangaje ko umuntu wese uzava muri Koreya y'Epfo azashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri ahantu hashyizweho na leta.
Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari batandukanye ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yakwitwara mu gihe cy'ibibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon ashinjwa ko leta itakemuye neza icyorezo cyangwa se bashima uko yabyitwayemo. Iki cyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byemera amategeko y'ibanze mu guhangana nacyo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bagaragaje impungenge ko ibyo bishobora gutuma ubutegetsi bwongera ububasha.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Hongiriya yatoye yemerera Minisitiri w'Intebe, Viktor Orbán, kuyobora binyuze mu itegeko kugeza igihe hazatangazwa andi mabwiriza, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko n'amatora no guhana umuntu wese ushinjwa gukwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma ku byerekeye virusi n'uburyo leta yakemuye iki kibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatewe n'ibihe byinshi by'imvura, bitewe n'uko ku isi hose hakoreshejwe ibikoresho byinshi byo kurwanya icyorezo, abantu bagura ibintu mu buryo bwo gutinya, n'ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho bihagarikwa.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze imiburo ku bijyanye n'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi kubera ko abakiriya bifuza cyane kandi abaguzi batabasha kuboneka.
Intara nyinshi kandi zahuye n'ubukene bw'ibicuruzwa by'ibanze, nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amacupa y'amazi, byavuye ku maduka, bituma habaho ubukene.
Urwego rw'ikoranabuhanga by'umwihariko rwamaganye ibyago byo gutinda kohereza ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki.
Dukurikije umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, ibisabwa mu bikoresho byo kwirinda byiyongereye inshuro 100.
Ibi byateje kuzamuka kw'ibiciro bikubye inshuro 20 ibiciro bisanzwe kandi byateje kandi ibitaramo byo gutanga ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byatinze amezi ane kugeza kuri atandatu.
Ibi kandi byatumye ibikoresho byo kwirinda bikena ku isi hose, kandi OMS iraburira ko bizashyira mu kaga abakozi b'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Uwo mushinga watumye amata y'abana aba make mu maduka manini, nyuma aza kubuzanywa na leta ya Ositaraliya. Nubwo umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wari mwinshi mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, kandi hakanabaho kwifuza cyane ibiribwa, utwo duce twombi ntitwigeze tugerwaho n'ikibazo gikomeye cyo kubura ibiribwa.
Ingamba zafashwe n'Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi n'ubwikorezi butemewe bw'ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi zagize ingaruka nziza, bityo birinda ibura ry'ibiribwa bikomeye byari byitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Kubera umusaruro munini w'ubuhinzi, mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani ntagabanuka ry'ingenzi ryabayeho, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera nk'uko byemezwa n'abahagarariye inganda.
Amaterasi y'ibiribwa yabaye ubusa by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi b'u Bushinwa batanze inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyo kurya bihagije.
Amategeko nk'ayo ariho mu Butaliyani asaba abahinzi b'ibiribwa kubika ibibatunga mu gihe habaye ibyago nk'ibyo.
Ingaruka mbi ku bukungu bw'isi zabaye nyinshi mu Bushinwa: raporo y'itangazamakuru yo ku ya 16 Werurwe yavuze ko ubukungu bw'u Bushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 bitewe n'ingamba zafashwe na leta zo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi, kandi ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwagabanutseho 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa bukomeye ari ikigo cy'ubukungu n'inganda, icyorezo cya virusi cyagaragaye ko ari ikibazo gikomeye cyugarije ubukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubukungu cya Economist Intelligence Unit, yavuze ko ibigo by'ubucuruzi bizakomeza guhungabana kugeza igihe hazabaho gusobanukirwa neza uko bizagenda.
Muri Mutarama 2020, hari abasesengura batekerezaga ko ingaruka z'icyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kurenga iz'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Impuguke muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis yavuze ko ingaruka ku ikoranabuhanga ku isi yose ishobora kuba miliyari zisaga 300 z'amadolari, ishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Umuryango w'ibihugu bitanga peteroli (OPEC) bivugwa ko  warasenyutse  nyuma y'igabanuka rikomeye ry'ibiciro bya peteroli bitewe n'ibyifuzo byagabanutse mu Bushinwa.
Amasoko y'imigabane ku isi yose yaragabanutse ku ya 24 Gashyantare bitewe n'ubwiyongere bukomeye bw'abanduye COVID-19 batari mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus, ibipimo byinshi by'imigabane muri Amerika birimo NASDAQ-100, S&amp;P 500 na Dow Jones Industrial Average byagize igabanuka rikomeye kuva mu 2008, Dow Jones igabanukaho amanota 1119, ikaba ari yo igabanuka rikomeye cyane ku munsi umwe kuva mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'imari mu 2007-08.
Ibipimo bitatu byose byasoje icyumweru bigabanutseho 10%.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje indangamuntu y'inguzanyo y'Ubushinwa ariko ikomeza kuba mbi.
Ibiciro by'imigabane byongeye kumanuka kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya Coronavirus, aho ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe ari bwo byagabanutse cyane.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu buzagabanuka.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu Mohamed El-Erian yashimye ingamba z'ibanze zafashwe mu gihe gikwiriye n'amabanki akomeye n'ibihugu.
Banki nkuru z'ibihugu zitabiriye vuba cyane kurusha uko zabikoze mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'imari ryo mu 2008.
Ubukerarugendo ni kimwe mu bice byazahajwe cyane n'ibihano byo kutajya mu mahanga, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, cyane cyane ahantu hatera ba mukerarugendo, ndetse n'amabwiriza ya leta yo kwirinda ingendo ku isi hose.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, kompanyi nyinshi z'indege zahagaritse ingendo kubera ko ibyifuzo byari byagabanutse, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas, mu gihe kompanyi y'indege y'akarere ya Flybe yo mu Bwongereza yasenyutse.
Ingaruka ku bucuruzi bw'amato y'ubwato bwageze ku rwego rutazwi mbere.
Ibigo byinshi by'indarayi n'ibigo by'amato na byo byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyahuriranye na Chunyun, igihe cy'ingenzi cy'ubukerarugendo gihuza n'Ubunani bw'Abashinwa.
Ibihe byinshi birimo abantu benshi byahagaritswe na guverinoma z'igihugu n'iz'uturere, harimo n'ibirori ngarukamwaka byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya, kandi ibigo byigenga na byo byafunze amaduka n'ahantu nyaburanga, nko muri Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Ibikorwa byinshi bijyanye n'Umwaka Mushya wa Lunar byahagaritswe kandi ahantu henshi hatemberezwa abantu harahagaritswe kugira ngo hatagira abantu benshi bahurira hamwe, harimo umujyi wa Beijing utemewe n'ibitaramo bya kera by'urusengero.
Mu ntara 24, uturere n'uturere 31 byo mu Bushinwa, abayobozi bongereye iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya kugeza ku ya 10 Gashyantare, bategeka ko ahantu henshi hakorerwa imirimo hatongera gufungura mbere y'uko iyo tariki igera.
Ibi bice byatanze 80% bya GDP y'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa mu mahanga.
Hong Kong yageze ku rwego rwo hejuru mu guhangana n'indwara zandura kandi itangaza ko ibintu byihutirwa, ifunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe kandi ihagarika iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya. Uruganda rw'ubucuruzi rw'ibikoresho rwatewe n'ingaruka ku isi hose, aho amaduka yagabanyijwe amasaha yo gufungura cyangwa agafungwa by'agateganyo.
Gusura abacuruzi mu Burayi na Amerika y'Amajyepfo byagabanutseho 40%.
Muri Amerika ya Ruguru no mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, abacuruzi babonye igabanuka rya 50 kugeza kuri 60 ku ijana.
Ibi kandi byatumye urujya n'uruza rw'abanyamaguru mu bigo by'ubucuruzi mu kwezi kwa gatatu rugabanukaho 33 kugeza kuri 43 ku ijana ugereranyije n'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare.
Abakora ibigo by'ubucuruzi ku isi hose bashyizeho izindi ngamba zirimo kongera igihe cyo gusukura, gushyiraho ibikoresho byo gupima ubushyuhe kugira ngo barebe ubushyuhe bw'abakiriya no guhagarika ibirori. Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye gishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Epfo gitekereza ko ikibazo cy'ubukene cyatewe n'icyorezo gishobora gutuma abantu bari hagati ya miliyoni 14 na 22 bongera kuba mu bukene bukabije muri Amerika y'Epfo ugereranyije n'aho nta cyorezo cyari gihari.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe icyorezo cyari ku isonga mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi kabo.
Mu Bushinwa, abenshi mu bakozi b'abimukira bo mu byaro bagera kuri miliyoni 300 bari mu mazu yabo mu ntara zo hagati cyangwa bari mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika basaga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi maze basaba leta ubufasha.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gutwara akazi ka miliyoni 47 muri Amerika, kandi umubare w'abashomeri ushobora kugera kuri 32%, nk'uko byemezwa na Banki y'Igihugu y'Igihugu y'Imiteguro ya Leta ya St. Louis. Gufunga mu Buhinde byatumye abakozi b'Abanyamahanga b'Abahinde babarirwa muri za miriyoni mirongo (bakorera umunsi umwe) batagira akazi. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ikigo Angus Reid bwagaragaje ko 44% by'ingo zo muri Kanada zari zagize ubushomeri. Abakozi hafi 900,000 batakaje akazi muri Esipanye kuva igihe hashyirwagaho gukumira mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati mu 2020.
Mu gice cya kabiri cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, abakozi b'Abafaransa miliyoni 4 basabye ubwishyu bw'abashomeri bw'agateganyo, abakozi b'Abongereza miliyoni 1 basabye inguzanyo rusange. Amashyirahamwe y'ubucuruzi agera hafi kuri miliyoni y'Abadage yafashe abakozi bayo bajya mu buryo bw'akazi k'igihe gito bufasha leta bwitwa Kurzarbeit.
Uburyo bw'ubudage bwo kwishyura abakozi bakora igihe gito bwashyizweho n'u Bufaransa n'Ubwongereza.
Urwego rw'ubuhanzi n'umurage w'umuco rwatewe cyane n'icyorezo, bigira ingaruka ku mikorere y'imiryango n'abantu ku isi hose, baba abikorera n'abikorera.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuhanzi n'umuco yagerageje gukomeza inshingano zayo (akenshi zitangwa na leta) zo guha umuryango uburenganzira bwo kubona umurage w'umuco, umutekano w'abakozi n'abaturage no gushyigikira abahanzi aho bishoboka.
Muri Werurwe 2020, hirya no hino ku isi mu byiciro bitandukanye, inzu ndangamurage, ibitabo, amazu y'imikino n'ibindi bigo by'umuco byafunzwe kugeza igihe habonetse ibindi bimenyetso, kandi imurika, ibikorwa n'ibitaramo byabyo byahagaritswe cyangwa byasubitswe.
Mu gusubiza, hakozwe ingamba zikomeye zo gutanga serivisi zindi hifashishijwe ikoranabuhanga. Ikindi cyatewe n'iki cyorezo cya vuba kandi cyihuta ni ukuhagarika ibikorwa by'idini, ibirori bikomeye bya siporo n'ibindi bikorwa by'iterambere, nk'ibirori by'umuziki n'ibitaramo, inama z'ikoranabuhanga n'imurika imideli.
Uruganda rwa sinema na rwo rwahuye n'ihungabana. Vatikani yatangaje ko ibirori byo kwizihiza Icyumweru gitagatifu i Roma, biba mu cyumweru cya nyuma cy'igihe cy'ubukristo cyo kwicuza ibyaha mu gihe cya Karema, byahagaritswe.
Diyosezi nyinshi zasabye abakristu bageze mu za bukuru kuguma mu ngo aho kujya mu misa ku cyumweru; amadini amwe n'amwe akwirakwiza amasengesho yabo kuri radiyo, kuri interineti no kuri televiziyo, mu gihe andi atanga amasengesho mu modoka.
Nk'uko diyosezi ya Roma Gatolika yafunze insengero zayo n'insengero zayo ndetse n'ahantu hitiriwe Mutagatifu Petero hatagira abakirisitu benshi bahita bajya gusenga, n'andi madini yahagaritse ibikorwa byayo kandi ahagarika amateraniro rusange mu nsengero, mu misigiti, mu masinagogi, mu nsengero no mu bigo by'amasengero.
Minisitiri w'Ubuzima wa Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu yahagaritswe mu duce twibasiwe n'icyorezo, kandi ko nyuma yaho ahantu hatagatifu hafunzwe, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abagenzi b'abanyamahanga n'abaturage bayo kwinjira mu duce dutagatifu twa Mecca na Medina.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye cyane mu mikino mpuzamahanga kuva mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi.
Imikino ikomeye yahagaritswe cyangwa yasubitswe, harimo UEFA Champions League 2019-20, Shampiyona y'Ubwongereza y'umupira w'amaguru 2019-20, UEFA Euro 2020, shampiyona ya NBA 2019-20 na shampiyona ya NHL 2019-20.
Iki cyorezo cyatumye imikino Olempike yo mu mpeshyi yo mu mwaka wa 2020 ihagarara, yari iteganyijwe gutangira mu mpera za Nyakanga; Komite Mpuzamahanga ya Olempiki yatangaje ku ya 24 Werurwe ko iyo mikino izasubikwa nyuma ya 2020, ariko bitarenze mu mpeshyi ya 2021.
Ibi byatumye abakinnyi benshi biyandikisha kuri interineti, kandi imbuga nyinshi z'imikino yo kuri interineti zabonye ukwiyongera gukomeye kw'umubare w'abashaka kwiyandikisha.
Amakinamico menshi akomeye, urugero nk'ayo kuri Broadway, na yo yahagaritse ibitaramo byose.
Bamwe mu bahanzi bashakishije uburyo bwo gukomeza gukora no gusangiza abandi ibihangano byabo kuri interineti mu buryo busimbura ibitaramo bisanzwe byabagaho, nk'ibitaramo byo kuri interineti no ku buryo bwa Live cyangwa  ibirori  byo kuri interineti byashyizweho kugira ngo abahanzi bashobore gukora, gukwirakwiza no kwamamaza ibihangano byabo.
Kuri interineti, abantu benshi bakunze kwifashisha interineti mu guseka no kwirangaza kubera ko nta cyizere gihari.
Kuva icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangira, abantu bo mu Bushinwa no muri Aziya y'Iburasirazuba, ndetse n'abo mu duce dukunze guhura n'ibibazo by'indwara muri Europe, Amerika n'ahandi, barushijeho kurengerwa, kwanga abanyamahanga no kubafata urwikekwe.
Hari ibintu byinshi by'ubwoba, gushidikanya n'ubugome byagiye bibaho mu bihugu byinshi, cyane cyane mu Burayi, Aziya y'iburasirazuba, Amerika ya Ruguru no mu karere ka Aziya na Pasifika.
Raporo zo mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare (igihe abenshi mu barwayi bari bakiri mu Bushinwa) zagaragaje ibyiyumvo by'ivangura rishingiye ku moko byagaragajwe n'amatsinda atandukanye ku isi hose ko Abashinwa bakwiriye iyi virusi cyangwa ko bahanwa mu buryo bukwiriye.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe bya Afurika na byo byabonye ko umwuka wo kurwanya Ubushinwa wiyongereye.
Abaturage benshi bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu ntara ya Hubei bavuze ko barenganurwa bitewe n'aho bakomoka.
Abashinwa bashyigikiwe, haba kuri interineti no hanze yayo, ndetse n'abatuye mu duce twatewe n'iyi virusi.
Kubera ko icyorezo cyateye mu bihugu bishya bishobora guhura n'iki cyorezo, Abataliyani, igihugu cya mbere mu Burayi cyibasiwe n'icyorezo gikomeye cya COVID-19, bashobora no gukekwaho ibyaha no kwanga abanyamahanga. Abaturage bo mu bihugu nka Maleziya, Nouvelle-Zélande, Singapuru na Koreya y'Epfo babanje gusinya impapuro zo gusaba ko Abashinwa batemerewe kwinjira mu gihugu cyabo mu rwego rwo guhagarika iki cyorezo.
Mu Buyapani, hashtag #ChineseDontComeToJapan yakomeje gukwirakwira kuri Twitter.
Abashinwa ndetse n'abandi bantu bo muri Aziya baba mu Bwongereza na Amerika batangaje ko ibitutsi by'ivangura rishingiye ku moko byiyongereye, ndetse n'ibitero.
Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Donald Trump yanenzwe cyane kubera ko yise coronavirus  virusi yo mu Bushinwa , ijambo ryakiriwe n'abamurwanyaga ko ridahuje ubwoko kandi ridakunda Abashinwa.
Muri Ukraine, abigaragambya bagabye igitero kuri bisi zitwaye abaturage ba Ukraine n'abanyamahanga bavuye mu byabo hagati ya Wuhan na Novi Sanzhary.
Abanyeshuri bo mu majyaruguru ashyira uburasirazuba bw'u Buhinde, buhana imbibi n'u Bushinwa, biga mu mijyi minini y'u Buhinde, bivugwa ko bakorewe ihohoterwa rishingiye ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Perezida w'ishyaka Bharatiya Janata mu ntara ya Bengal y'iburengerazuba Dilip Ghosh yavuze ko Abashinwa basenye ibidukikije kandi niyo mpamvu Imana yabahaye igihano .
Nyuma yaho, ibyo byavuzwe n'ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe ububanyi n'amahanga kiri i Kolkata byamaganiwe nabi, bivuga ko ari  ibinyoma . Mu Bushinwa, urwikekwe rw'abanyamahanga n'ivangura rishingiye ku moko ku baturage batari Abashinwa byongerewe n'icyorezo, abanyamahanga bagaragazwa nk'  imyanda y'abanyamahanga  ikwiye  kurandurwa .
Ibinyamakuru byinshi bishyura amafaranga byabikuyeho kubera amakuru yose cyangwa amwe mu makuru yavugaga kuri coronavirus.
