Gupima indwara y'ubuhumekero ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano harimo uburyo bwo gupima virusi no gupima abasirikare b'umubiri bakomoka mu guhangana n'ubwandu.
Kuba virusi iri mu bipimo byemezwa na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya koronavirusi.
Iyi isuzuma yagenewe mu buryo bwihariye kureba gusa RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu buherutse cyane cyangwa bukomeje.
Kugaragaza abanduye (serologie) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo batabivuga cyangwa abadafite ibimenyetso.
Ibipimo by'urupfu rw'indwara n'urwego rw'ubudahangarwa mu bantu bishobora kumenyekana hakurikijwe ibivuye muri ubu bushakashatsi.
Kubera gupima kutagira ingano, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bwa virusi mu baturage bacyo muri Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoze ibizamini ku bantu barenga 3%, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini ku mubare w'ibizamini byagiye bikorwa mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Ibi bishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa, ishobora kuba yararenze cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hakoreshejwe inyandiko isubiramo ikurikirwa n'imikorere ya polymerization mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR), ikizamini gishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe hifashishijwe uburyo butandukanye, harimo no gukoresha isuku y'amazuru cyangwa ibipimo by'amahembe.
Ibisubizo bikunze kugaragara mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi 2.
Igishushanyo cya RT-PCR cyakozwe hakoreshejwe udukingirizo tw'umunwa ni icyo kwizerwa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ishobora kuva mu muhogo ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bapimwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, ibipimo bishobora gutorwa mu nzira y'ubuhumekero bwimbitse hakoreshejwe imashini yo gukoramo, cyangwa se hakakoreshwa amacandwe.
Imwe mu miti ya mbere ya PCR yakozwe na Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 ikoresheje inyandiko isubiramo ikurikirwa n'imikorere ya polymerization mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR), ikaba yarashingiye ku bikoresho 250.000 byatanzwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwakoze ikizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Sosiyete yo muri Koreya y'Epfo yitwa Kogenebiotech yakoze ibikoresho byo gupima SARS-CoV-2 byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi bishingiye kuri PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus) ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Ibona ubwoko bwa  E  busangirwa na virusi ya koronavirusi ya beta yose, n'ubwoko bwa RdRp bwihariye bwa SARS-CoV-2.Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni imwe mu masosiyete ya mbere yahawe uruhushya rwo kwihutisha na China National Medical Products Administration rwo gukoresha igikoresho cya PCR mu gupima SARS-CoV-2. Muri Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga ibikoresho byacyo bya RT-PCR byo gupima Coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) mu gihe nyacyo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi binyuze mu ikigo ReinterInternational Resource.
Mu mashini za mbere z'ibizamini, kimwe cya gatatu cy'ibizamini byagenewe byabaga bidatanga umusaruro ushimishije kubera ko byabaga birimo imiti itavuguruza, kandi hari n'ikibazo cy'ibizamini byabaga byarahagaritswe muri CDC i Atlanta. Ibyo byatumye mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare 2020, ingero ziri munsi ya 100 z'ibizamini ku munsi zikorwa neza.
Ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri ntibyari byemewe kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, ari bwo laboratwari za leta n'iz'ibanze zemerewe gutangira gupima.
Iki cyemezo cyemejwe n'ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti ku buryo bw'ibanze. Laboratwari z'ubucuruzi muri Amerika zatangiye gupima mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko ibizamini bya COVID-19 bishingiye kuri RT-PCR biboneka mu gihugu hose.
Quest Diagnostics kandi yatanze ibizamini bya COVID-19 mu gihugu cyose ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta mugambi wo kugabanya umubare w'ibipimo watangajwe. Gukusanya ibipimo no kubitunganya bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ikizamini cya COVID-19 cyakozwe kandi gitangwa n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubushakashatsi mu by'Ubwanditsi bw'Ubwandu n'Ikoranabuhanga mu Binyabuzima VECTOR.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, iki kizamini cyanditswe n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Ubuziranenge mu by'Ubuzima. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, byatangajwe ko Ivuriro rya Mayo ryatangije ikizamini cyo gutahura ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3,5 mu bipimo byinshi, bityo igikoresho kimwe kikaba gishobora gukora ibizamini bigera ku 4,128 mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yahaye Abbott Laboratories uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (USA) mu igerageza ry'urwo rukingo rwa Abbott m2000. FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya nk'urwo mbere ku bigo bya Hologic, LabCorp na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid kandi yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini cyamaze iminota 45.
