Gukaraba intoki, nanone bita isuku y'intoki, ni ugukuraho imyanda, ibinure, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe mu gukaraba intoki.
Gukaraba intoki buri gihe n'isabuni mu "bihe by'ingenzi" by'umunsi, bifasha kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ibiheri na kolera, zikwirakwizwa mu kanwa n'ibinure.
Umuntu ashobora kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane, urugero nko kudakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa (ni ukuvuga mu maso).
Ni ngombwa gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu bihe bitanu by'ingenzi by'umunsi: mbere na nyuma yo gusama, nyuma yo gusukura ibere ry'umwana cyangwa kumuhindurira amasahani, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko zikiri nto.
Niba udafite amazi n'isabune mu ntoki, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje imyanda. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) risaba ko ukaraba intoki:
mbere, mu gihe no nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro;
mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye;
nyuma yo guhindurira umwana inda cyangwa gukaraba umwana umaze kujya mu bwiherero;
nyuma yo kwitsamura cyangwa gukorora/gusinzira;
nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ibiryo by'amatungo cyangwa imyanda y'amatungo;
Isuku y'intoki mu buvuzi ni uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima bw'abantu mu gihe bakora ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kwita ku barwayi bishobora kwirinda cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi ni ukuvanaho udukoko dutera indwara (bakteriya, virusi cyangwa ibindi bintu bishobora gutera indwara) n'imiti ishobora kwangiza cyangwa gutera indwara.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakoresha ibiribwa cyangwa bakora mu buvuzi, ariko no ku baturage muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bigira akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara zitandura; gukumira indwara zandura zitera igifu; kugabanya ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero;
kandi bigabanya umubare w'abana bapfa babyarira mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko kongera isuku y'intoki bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu barushaho gukura neza.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero n'iseru ushobora kugabanuka mu gihe hakozwe impinduka zoroheje mu myitwarire, nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyo myitozo yoroshye ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bazize izo ndwara ugera hafi kuri 50%.
Gushyiraho ingamba zo gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya indwara z'ibiheri ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, urugero rusa n'urwo umuntu yahabwa n'amazi meza yo kunywa mu duce dukennye.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabuni bigabanya indwara z'ibiheri ku kigero cya 48%, kandi ni bwo buryo bwiza kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda ibicurane n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (IRA). Ni igikorwa kigomba gukorwa mu buryo bw'ibanze mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Imyotsi, imwe mu mpamvu z'ingenzi zitera indwara y'ubuhumekero, ni yo mpamvu ya mbere ihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, ihitana abagera kuri miliyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'igifu n'umusonga hamwe bihitana abana bagera kuri miliyoni 3,5 buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko kugira akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki n'isabuni mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero bishobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha inkingo cyangwa uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kuvura, kandi bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abapfa bishwe n'indwara y'ibisebe n'icyiciro cya kane cy'abapfa bishwe n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi bijyana n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku mu gihe cy'imishinga y'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki birinda kandi impetigo, yandura binyuze mu guhura n'umuntu imbonankubone.
Ingaruka mbi cyane, ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora kwangiza uruhu bigatuma rukomera.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danemark mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera eczema cyangwa indwara y'uruhu mu ntoki, zigaragaramo uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu n'urwicurama, kandi bikunze kugaragara cyane mu bakora mu by'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane kandi bivugwa ko ari kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumyi (OCD).
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni ngombwa mu bihe bitanu by'ingenzi by'umunsi kugira ngo bigabanya ubwandu bw'indwara z'umunwa: mbere na nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (gukorora, gutakaza), nyuma yo gusukura amabere y'umwana (cyangwa guhindura indabo), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gutunganya inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko zikiri nto.
Gukaraba intoki neza ni ngombwa kandi mu kwirinda kwandura indwara, cyane cyane mbere na nyuma yo gukira igikomere cyangwa igikomere, nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura, nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa gukorana n'amatungo no nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, umubare w'abantu biyuhagira intoki n'isabune ni muto.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2015 ku isuku y'intoki mu bihugu 54 bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo, ingo 38,7% zikoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabia Saoudite ari yo ifite igipimo kiri hejuru (97%), Amerika iri hagati (77%), naho Ubushinwa bukaba ari bwo bufite igipimo kiri hasi (23%). Ubu hari uburyo bwinshi bwo guhindura imyitwarire no gushyiraho demokarasi mu gukoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki mu bihe by'ingenzi by'umunsi. Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, birashoboka cyane ko abana bo mu mashuri biga mu matsinda bakaraba intoki mu bihe runaka by'umunsi kugira ngo abana bagire akamenyero ko kubikora.
