Nyamara, umubare muto w'abantu bakaraba intoki ushobora guterwa n'ingeso z'ingeso mbi, aho guterwa n'ibura ry'amazi n'isabune.
Guteza imbere gukaraba intoki n'isabune no gukora ibikorwa byo kumenyekanisha ibi bishobora guhindura imyanzuro ya politiki, kumenyekanisha ibyiza by'iyo myitozo no guhindura imyitwarire y'abaturage mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bigerweho, hakenewe ibikorwa byo gukurikirana no gusuzuma.
Isesengura ryakozwe ku buryo buhoraho ku bushakashatsi 70, ryagaragaje ko uburyo bwo mu karere bw'igihugu bugira ingaruka nziza mu kongera umubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abicisha make, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bwo kwamamaza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga butagira ingaruka nziza. Mu rwego rwo guteza imbere gukaraba intoki mu mashuri, urugero ni "Inzira y'inyenyeri eshatu" ya UNICEF, itera amashuri inkunga yo gufata ingamba zoroshye kandi zidakora amafaranga menshi zo kureba neza ko abanyeshuri bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune, kandi bubahiriza andi mabwiriza y'isuku.
