Kubaka aho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo guteza imbere isuku y'intoki bigamije kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo kumenyekanisha ibikorwa bigamije guhindura imyitwarire. Nyuma y'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-2020, UNICEF yashishikarije abantu gukoresha emoji zigaragaza gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwibanze ku ngaruka rusange zo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere ugereranyije n'imyaka y'ubuzima buzira umuze yagezweho (ni ukuvuga DALY zirinzwe).
