Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu, cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibibazo nk'ababyeyi baherutse kubyara cyangwa abasirikare bakomerekeye mu bitaro, cyamenyekanye bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 hagati n'abahanga babiri mu isuku y'intoki: umuganga w'Umunya-Hongiriya Ignaz Semmelweis wakoreraga i Vienne muri Autriche na Florence Nightingale, w'Umwongereza washinze ubuvuzi bugezweho.
Muri icyo gihe, abantu benshi bari bacyizera ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi cyane zitwa miasma.
Mu myaka ya 1980, ibyorezo by'indwara ziterwa n'ibiribwa n'indwara z'indwara z'indwara z'indwara z'indwara zatumye Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara gitera inkunga y'isuku y'intoki nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cya grippe porcine mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye mu bihugu byinshi abantu barushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune mu kwirinda izi ndwara zitandura.
Urugero, mu Budage, ibyapa bigaragaza  uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki  byashyizwe iruhande rw'imisanzu yo mu bwiherero rusange no mu bwiherero bw'amazu y'ibiro n'ibibuga by'indege.
Imvugo  gukaraba intoki  yerekeza ku kwanga umuntu kwemera inshingano cyangwa kuba umufasha w'ikintu runaka.
Iryo jambo rikomoka ku murongo wo muri Bibiliya wo muri Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yoza intoki ze ku cyemezo cyo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko iryo jambo ryakwirakwijwe cyane mu baturage bamwe na bamwe b'Icyongereza.
Mu gitabo cya Shakespeare, Macbeth, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki mu buryo butagoragozwa mu kugerageza gusukura ikizinga cy'ibitekerezo, ikimenyetso cy'umutimanama we mubi ku byaha yakoze kandi yatumye umugabo we akora.
