Mu bikorwa byo kurwanya ibyago muri iri tsinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo guhumeka neza ukoresheje ibikoresho bikingira umwuka, amadirishya y'isuku no gutanga ibikoresho byo kwirinda mu gihe uhuye n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
