Ibipimo by'ibyago bikwiye kuri abo bakozi birimo ibipimo by'ikoranabuhanga nk'ibyumba by'umwuka bihumanya kandi bikoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bikwiye.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutaba bari mu kazi kubera ko barwaye, bagomba kwita ku bandi cyangwa batinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Imikorere y'ubucuruzi ishobora guhinduka haba mu bijyanye n'ibicuruzwa bisabwa ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubikuraho (urugero, kugura ibintu hanze y'amasaha y'ikirenga cyangwa gukoresha serivisi zo gutanga cyangwa gutwara imodoka).
Byongeye kandi, kohereza ibicuruzwa mu turere twibasiwe cyane na COVID-19 bishobora guhagarikwa. Gahunda yo kwitegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura ishobora gukoreshwa nk'ubuyobozi bw'ingamba zo kwirinda.
Imigambi ijyanye n'ibyago byo kurwara indwara ziterwa n'imiterere y'akazi n'imikorere, harimo aho umuntu ahurira n'ibiza, ibyago byo mu muryango n'ibyago byo mu baturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo, urugero nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Nanone kandi, bagaragaza uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyo byago n'imigambi y'ubutabazi ku bibazo bishobora kuvuka bitewe n'ibyorezo.
Gahunda zo gutegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura zishobora kuba ingingo z'inama z'igihugu cyangwa iz'akarere.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ubwandu mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bandi bantu mu nganda zabo.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ikigo giherereye bugira ingaruka ku bisubizo bikoreshwa.
Urwego rwo kugenzura ibyago ni urwego rukoreshwa mu rwego rw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi kugira ngo hashyirweho gahunda yo kugenzura ibyago hakurikijwe ubushobozi.
Iyo ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwiza bwo kugenzura ni ubuhanga, hakurikirwa n'ubuyobozi, hanyuma ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
Kugenzura ikoranabuhanga bikubiyemo kugabanya abakozi ibyago by'akazi, aho gushingira ku myitwarire y'abakozi.
Igenzura ry'ubuyobozi ni impinduka mu miyoborere cyangwa mu mikorere y'akazi isaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidakora neza cyane ugereranyije n'ibipimo by'ikoranabuhanga n'ibikorwa, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda bimwe mu bintu bishobora gutuma umuntu ahura n'ibiza.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa hakurikijwe ibyago bishobora kugera ku mukozi, bukagirwa uko bikwiye (urugero nk'udupfukamunwa), bukambara neza kandi buhoraho, bukagenzurwa buri gihe, bukitabwaho kandi bugasimbuzwa aho bikenewe, kandi bukurwaho, bukarindwa kandi bugatunganywa neza cyangwa bukarandurwa kugira ngo hatabaho kwanduzwa.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano (OSHA), akazi gashobora guteza indwara mu buryo buciriritse gafite uburyo buke bwo guhura n'abantu n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zisabwa ahantu hose hakorerwa imirimo zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo barwaye, gushyiraho amategeko yo guhumeka, harimo no gupfuka umunwa n'amazuru mu gihe bakoroye no kwitsamura, gutanga utwenda two gukarabya no gutwara imyanda, kwitegura gukora ku muhanda cyangwa gukora amasaha anyuranye igihe bibaye ngombwa, kubuza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi no gukomeza isuku n'imiti y'ubuvuzi mu kazi.
Kumenya no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwandura vuba ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitegeka abakozi bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bafite umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 batakoresheje imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa imiti igabanya ibimenyetso. Bategeka kandi gushyiraho politiki z'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara zihendutse, kwemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bita kuri umwe mu bagize umuryango urwaye no kumenyesha abakozi ayo mabwiriza.
