Uruhare rw'inyuma y'ingirabuzimafatizo rwa ACE2 rugabanywa n'urundi rugingo rwa sheddase, uru rugingo rw'imyanda rugafungurwa mu maraso, hanyuma rukasohoka mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi: ACE2 ifatanye n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo cyane cyane mu ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu bwonko bw'ubuhumekero bw'ubwoko bwa II, uturemangingo tw'ubwonko duto, uturemangingo tw'amaraso n'utw'imiyoboro y'amaraso, n'uturemangingo tw'amaraso mu bice by'umubiri byinshi.
