ACE2 nayo ihindura amino acide phenylamine ifite karubokisi ya angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) maze ikayivamo angiotensin ikomeza imitsi (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
LACE2 ishobora kandi gutandukanya izindi peptides nyinshi zirimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, lapelin, neurotensin, dynorphine A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igenzura uburyo umubiri ukoresha umutobe wa SLC6A19 utwara aside ya amino kandi ifitanye isano n'indwara ya Hartnup.
Kubera ko ACE2 ari poroteyine y'uruhu, ni yo nzira y'ibanze yo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi ituma SARS ibaho) na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi ituma COVID-19 ibaho).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 n'urwego rwa enzymatic rwa ACE2 ku gice cy'imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo bigatuma habaho kwinjiza virusi na enzymes mu bice by'imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
