Byongeye kandi,  ibyago byo kurwara ibicurane byaragabanutse no mu barwayi bavurwaga ACE inhibitor bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara ibicurane, cyane cyane abafite indwara y'umutima n'indwara y'umutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors nabyo byahujwe no kugabanya impfu ziterwa n'ibicurane, nubwo ibipimo by'ibicurane bitari bikomeye cyane ugereranyije n'ibimenyetso by'ibicurane muri rusange.
