Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za telefoni zigenewe gufasha abantu kumenya abo bahuye na bo mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, ni ukuvuga kumenya abantu (abo bahuye) bashobora kuba baragiranye isano n'umuntu wanduye.
Porogaramu zitandukanye zarakorewe cyangwa zatanzwe, zifite inkunga yemewe na leta mu turere tumwe na tumwe no mu nzego zimwe na zimwe.
Ibikoresho byinshi byatangiye gukorwa mu rwego rwo gukora porogaramu zo gukurikirana abakoraho.
Izi gahunda, cyane cyane izishingira ku gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari, zitera ibibazo bijyanye no kubahiriza ubuzima bwite.
Hari ubundi buryo butari bubangamiye, harimo gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugira ngo umenye aho umuntu ari hafi n'izindi telefoni zigendanwa.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ku mugaragaro ko bagiye gushyira mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu zabo z'imikorere Android na iOS, uburyo bwo gushyigikira izi porogaramu za Bluetooth.
Leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay bashyize mu Bushinwa porogaramu ituma abaturage bamenya niba barigeze guhura n'abantu barwaye COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa, naho Singapore yo ihitamo porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Ryateguwe n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu ikoranabuhanga ryo muri ako karere, ryatanzwe nk'ifunguye kandi rizatangwa na leta. Macedonia ya Ruguru yatangije  StopKorona! , porogaramu ya Bluetooth ikurikirana ubwandu bw'abantu bashobora kuba baranduye kandi ikorana n'inzego z'ubuzima mu buryo bwihuse.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kuva ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu bari mu ngendo z'iterambere igeze kure kandi ishobora gutangira gukoreshwa mu byumweru bike biri imbere. Porogaramu nk'iyo irateganywa gukoreshwa muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa ( StopCovid).
Australia na Nouvelle-Zélande bitegura gushyiraho porogaramu zigendera kuri TraceTogether muri Singapuru zishingiye kuri BlueTrace. Uburusiya bushaka gushyiraho porogaramu yo kumenya aho umuntu ari mu gihe avuwe ko afite COVID-19 kandi atuye i Moscou, kugira ngo bumve ko atava mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu w'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu gukoresha uburyo bushingiye ku bikoresho, harimo ibyiza by'ibinyoma n'ubushobozi buke mu gihe igice gito cy'abaturage ari bo bakoresha ikoranabuhanga.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry'ibikorwa by'ikoranabuhanga  bya koronavirusi  by'ibinyoma cyangwa byangiza, Apple yemerera gusa ibigo  byemewe  cyangwa byiringirwa by'ibanze kongera porogaramu zijyanye na koronavirusi kuri App Store.
Google na Amazon byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashinzwe kurinda ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka za porogaramu za koronavirusi ku isuzuma ry'abantu benshi, cyane cyane ko ibikorwa by'ubugenzuzi byashyizweho mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya koronavirusi bishobora gusenyuka igihe icyorezo kizaba kimaze kuvaho.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura bugabanuka.
Ayo mashyirahamwe yashyizeho ibintu umunani bigomba kubahirizwa mu mishinga ya leta:
Igenzura rigomba kuba  ryemewe n'amategeko, rikenewe kandi ryihariye ;
Itegeko rigena uburyo bwo kugenzura no kugenzura rigomba kuba rikubiyemo ingingo zo kureka;
ikoreshwa ry'amakuru rigomba kuba rigamije kurwanya COVID-19 gusa;
umutekano w'amakuru n'ubwisungane mu makuru bigomba kurindwa mu buryo bugaragara;
Igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga rigomba kureba neza ko ridakomeza ivangura n'amacakubiri;
gusangira amakuru n'abantu batatu bigomba gushyirwa mu mategeko;
hakwiye kubaho uburyo bwo kurinda abaturage no kubakurikirana mu gihe habaye ihohoterwa;
 uruhare rukomeye  rw'abari mu nzego zose  z'ibanze  ruzaba rukenewe, cyane cyane inzobere mu by'ubuzima bwa rubanda n'imiryango itari ifite aho ibogamiye.
Gahunda Google/Apple itegura igamije gukemura ikibazo cy'ubugenzuzi bukomeje binyuze mu gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana muri sisitemu y'imikorere y'ibikoresho byabo iyo bitakiri ngombwa.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byakoresheje uburyo bwo kumenya aho umuntu ari mu muyoboro aho gukoresha porogaramu, bivanaho icyifuzo cyo gukuramo porogaramu kandi bikanavanaho ubushobozi bwo kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Israel, uburyo bwo gushakisha imbuga za interineti bwemewe.
Ibisubizo by'urusobe bifite amakuru y'aho uherereye (GPS) bifite ibibazo bikomeye bishobora kuvuka mu bijyanye n'ibanga.
Ariko, ntabwo sisitemu zose zishingiye kuri seriveri z'ibanze zikeneye kubona amakuru yerekeye ahantu umuntu ari; sisitemu nyinshi zashyizweho muburyo bwo gukoresha seriveri z'ibanze gusa kugirango zihure, bityo bigatuma byubahiriza ubuzima bwite (reba igice gikurikira).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshejwe uburyo butari kuri porogaramu mu gukurikirana abo bahuye.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, iyi sisitemu yakusanyije amakuru yo gukurikirana mu bintu bitandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya telefoni n'amakarita, hanyuma bayashyira hamwe kugira ngo yohereze imiburo binyuze kuri SMS ku bantu bashobora kuba baranduye.
Uretse gukoresha aya makuru kugira ngo aburire abantu bashobora kuba baragize aho bahuriye n'abandi, leta yashyizeho uburyo bwo gutanga amakuru y'aho umuntu ari, ibyo bikaba byaratumye amategeko yo kurinda amabanga y'amakuru ahinduka cyane nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS.
