Ibisobanuro by'ibyo bitaratangazwaga ku ya 6 Mata 2020.
Gukurikirana abakoresha telefoni mu buryo bufite ibanga ni igitekerezo cyemewe, gishyigikiwe n'ubumenyi bwinshi bw'ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2013. Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'abahanga arenga 12 yakoraga ku buryo bwo kurinda ubuzima bwite, harimo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kugira ngo bandike aho umuntu ari hafi y'izindi telefoni zigendanwa.
Ariko, umushinga wa PEPP-PT ni igikorwa cyo guhuza ibintu, gihuza uburyo bw'ibanze n'ubw'ibanze, ntabwo ari uburyo bumwe. Ubu buryo butandukanye burimo Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Temporary Contact Numbers (TCN, yahoze yitwa Contact Event Numbers, CEN), Privacy Sensitive Protocols na Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT), n'ibindi.
Izi protocole zituma umwirondoro w'umuntu ku giti cye utazigera uva ku gikoresho kandi ko ibintu byose bihuza bikorwa ku gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'ibanga rya MIT Media Lab ubu ririmo gukora SafePaths, urubuga rukoresha uburyo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite mu gukusanya no gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari cyangwa yo kuvugana kugira ngo bakurikirane ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Ubu buryo bushingiye ku bushakashatsi bw'igitabo cyitwa  Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic  cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Urupapuro rwa SafeTrace rwakozwe na  Enigma MPC, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga rishinzwe kubungabunga ubuzima bwite cyashinzwe bwa mbere muri MIT Media Lab, ni ikindi gikorwa nk'icyo.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho bifite umutekano kugira ngo abakoresha bashobore gusangira amakuru y'aho bari n'amakuru y'ubuzima n'abandi bakoresha n'abategetsi, ariko batagomba guhungabanya ibanga ry'amakuru.
