COVID-19 yamenyekanye mu Kuboza 2019.
Icyorezo gikomeye cyadutse ku isi yose mu mwaka wa 2020, bituma hashyirwaho amafaranga menshi n'ubushakashatsi mu gukora urukingo.
Imiryango myinshi ikoresha ibinyabuzima byasohotse mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga mu gukora inkingo zishobora gukoreshwa mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Mu kwezi kwa kane, CEPI yavuze ko igomba gukora vuba, ikagira ubushobozi bwo gukora, ikagera ku bantu benshi kandi ikabaha urukingo ku isi hose.
Muri Mata, abahanga mu bya siyansi bo muri CEPI batangaje ko ibigo 10 bitandukanye by'ikoranabuhanga biri gukora ubushakashatsi no guteza imbere imishinga mu ntangiriro za 2020 hagamijwe gukora urukingo rukora neza rwa COVID-19.
Intego z'urubuga rukomeye zigiye mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'umutekano zirimo:
acide nucleic (DNA na RNA) (icyiciro cya mbere: ikorwa n'umukandida w'urukingo: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
virusi (icyiciro cya mbere: umushinga n'urukingo rw'indwara: CanSino Biologics, virusi itera adenovirus ya 5
Nk'uko abahanga mu bya siyansi ba CEPI babivuze muri Mata, inkingo 115 z'abakandida ziri mu byiciro bya mbere by'iterambere, 78 (79 nk'uko ikigo cya Milken kibitangaza) zemejwe ko zikorera, naho izindi 37 zatangajwe, ariko amakuru make cyane y'abantu bose arahari (akekwa ko ari mu igenamigambi cyangwa mu buryo).
Icyiciro cya mbere n'icya kabiri cy'igerageza gikora igerageza ry'ibanze ry'umutekano n'irwanya indwara, akenshi rifatwa mu buryo butunguranye, rigenzurwa n'ikoreshwa ry'imiti y'isukari, kandi rikorerwa mu bigo byinshi, rigamije kumenya neza ibipimo by'indwara.
Ibizamini byo mu cyiciro cya III bikunze kuba birimo abantu benshi, harimo n'itsinda ry'abashinzwe kugenzura, kandi bikagerageza ubushobozi bw'urukingo mu kwirinda indwara, mu gihe hagenzurwa ingaruka mbi ku gipimo cyiza.
Mu bantu 79 bari mu bikorwa byo gukora inkingo (bemejwe mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020), 74 ntibari mu cyiciro cyo gupima abantu (baracyari mu bushakashatsi  bw'ibanze ).
