Gukoresha imashini zo guhumeka birushaho kugorana iyo umuntu afite indwara y'ubuhumekero budafite ubushobozi (ARDS) mu gihe cya COVID-19 kandi guhumeka umwuka wa ogisijeni birushaho kugorana.
Imashini z'ubuhumekero zifite uburyo bwo kugenzura umuvuduko n'imbaraga nyinshi z'umwuka (PEEP) ni ngombwa kugira ngo haboneke umwuka wa ogisijeni uhagije kandi hagabanywe ibyago byo kwangirika kw'ibihaha biterwa n'ubuhumekero n'indwara ya pneumothorax.
PEEP iri hejuru ishobora kuba itaboneka ku bikoresho bya kera byo guhumeka.
Ubushakashatsi ku miti ishobora gukoreshwa bwatangiye muri Mutarama 2020 kandi hari imiti myinshi ya virusi iri kugeragezwa mu buvuzi.
Remdesivir isa n'aho ari yo ifite icyizere kurusha izindi.
Nubwo imiti mishya ishobora kutaboneka mbere ya 2021, hari imiti myinshi irimo kugeragezwa yamaze kwemerwa mu bindi bikoresho kandi igeragezwa riratangiye.
Umuti urwanya virusi ushobora kugeragezwa ku bantu barwaye indwara ikomeye.
OMS yasabye ko abitangiye gukora imirimo bajya mu igerageza ku buvuzi bushobora gukoreshwa no ku buvuzi butari bubi. FDA yahaye uruhushya rw'agateganyo plasma y'abantu bakize nk'ubuvuzi bw'igerageza mu gihe ubuzima bw'umuntu buri mu kaga gakomeye cyangwa ka hafi.
Ntabwo byakozwe mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi rikenewe kugira ngo byemezwe ko nta cyo bitwaye kandi ko bikora neza mu kuvura iyi ndwara.
Muri Gashyantare 2020, Ubushinwa bwatangije porogaramu yo gukoresha kuri telefoni igenewe guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
