Perezida wa Estonia, Kersti Kaljulaid, yasabye isi yose gushaka uburyo bushya bwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Abantu bashobora guhura n'ibibazo by'igenzurwa, kugabanya ingendo, ingaruka z'ubuvuzi cyangwa gutinya ubwandu ubwabwo.
BBC yasubiyemo amagambo ya Rory O'Connor avuga ko:  kwicamo ibice, irungu, guhangayika ku buzima, guhangayika no guhungabana k'ubukungu ari ibintu by'ingenzi cyane mu kwangiza ubuzima bwo mu mutwe n'imibereho myiza y'abantu .
Iyi ndwara ishobora kuba yoroheje, nta bimenyetso byinshi cyangwa se nta bimenyetso, bisa n'izindi ndwara zisanzwe z'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane.
Ubusanzwe abantu bafite uburwayi buciriritse bakira mu byumweru bibiri, mu gihe abanduye cyane cyangwa bafite uburwayi bukomeye bakira mu byumweru bitatu kugeza kuri bitandatu.
Abagore batwite bashobora kugira ibyago byinshi byo kwandura COVID-19 bikomeye hakurikijwe amakuru y'ubwandu bw'indwara nk'iyi, nka SARS na MERS, ariko nta makuru ahagije ahari ku bijyanye na COVID-19. Mu bihe bimwe na bimwe, COVID-19 ishobora kugira ingaruka ku bihaha kandi igateza amapfupfa.
Mu barwayi cyane, COVID-19 ishobora kwihuta igatera indwara y'ubuhumekero budafite ubushobozi (ARDS) ituma umuntu adashobora guhumeka neza, akagira ikibazo cyo kubura umwuka cyangwa se agakomereka mu ngingo.
Ibibazo biterwa na COVID-19 birimo impiswi, ibibazo byo kuvura amaraso, n'ibikomere by'umutima, impyiko n'umwijima.
Indwara zo kuvura amaraso, cyane cyane kongera igihe cyo kuvura za prothrombin, byagaragaye kuri 6% by'abarwaye COVID-19 bajyanwa mu bitaro, naho 4% by'abafite iyi ndwara bagaragaza ko impyiko zabo zidakora neza.
Hafi ya 20 kugeza kuri 30% by'abantu barwaye COVID-19 bafite intungamubiri nyinshi mu gifu (transaminases).
Raporo imwe n'iyo yavuze ko hagati y'igihe ibimenyetso byatangiriye no gupfa, haheze iminsi icumi, kandi ko batanu muri bo bari mu bitaro.
Ariko, abarwayi bahinduriwe mu bitaro bya ICU bari bafite iminsi irindwi yo kuva mu bitaro kugeza bapfuye.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi bakuru, igihe cy'ikirenga hagati y'ibimenyetso byo gutangira no gupfa cyari iminsi 14, aho iminsi yose yari hagati y'itandatu n'iminsi 41.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ubushakashatsi ku buzima mu Bushinwa (NHC), abagabo bapfaga ku kigero cya 2,8%, mu gihe abagore bapfaga ku kigero cya 1,7%.
Ibizamini bya histopathologique byakozwe nyuma y'urupfu rw'ibipimo by'ibihaha byerekanye ko hari ibyangiritse mu bice by'ibihaha, hamwe n'imyanda y'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha byombi.
Impinduka mu miterere ya virusi yagaragaye mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Igishushanyo cy'ibihaha gisa n'ikibazo cy'ubuhumekero budafite imbaraga (ARDS).
Mu bantu 11,8% bapfuye bashyizwe ahagaragara na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa, basanze umutima uhagaze nabi bitewe n'umubare munini wa troponin cyangwa umutima uhagaze.
Amakuru yo muri Werurwe aturuka muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, agaragaza ko 89% by'abari barwariye mu bitaro bari bafite uburwayi bw'ibanze. Kubona imiti n'imimerere y'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage mu karere bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bipfa.
Ibipimo by'ubwandu bw'iyo ndwara bigenda bitandukana bitewe n'ubwo butandukaniro mu turere, ariko nanone bitewe n'ibibazo by'uburyo.
Kuba abantu barwaye indwara zidakomeye cyane ari bake bishobora gutuma umubare w'abapfa urushaho kwiyongera.
Icyakora, kuba abantu bapfa bazize abanduye mbere bishobora kugaragaza ko umubare w'abapfa ubu utagereranywa.
Abanywa itabi bari bafite ibyago byo kugaragaza ibimenyetso bikomeye bya COVID-19 bikubye inshuro 1,4 kandi bari bafite ibyago byo kujya mu bitaro byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane cyangwa gupfa bikubye inshuro 2,4 ugereranyije n'abatanywa itabi. Hari n'impungenge z'ingaruka z'igihe kirekire z'iyo ndwara.
Ubuyobozi bw'ibitaro bya Hong Kong bwagaragaje ko ubushobozi bwo guhumeka bwagabanutseho hagati ya 20% na 30% mu bantu bamwe na bamwe bakize indwara, kandi ibipimo byo mu bihaha bigaragaza ko hari ibyangiritse ku mubiri.
Ibi kandi bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cyo kurwara indwara z'indwara z'ubuhumekero nyuma yo gukira.
Muri Werurwe 2020, ntibyari bizwi niba ubwandu bw'imyanya ndangagitsina bwigeze butuma abantu barwaye indwara bakira bagira ubudahangarwa bw'igihe kirekire.
Ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara bufatwa nk'ubushyize mu gaciro, hashingiwe ku myitwarire y'izindi koronavirusi, ariko hari abantu bakira COVID-19 nyuma bagaragayeho coronavirus nyuma yaho.
Ibi bifatwa nk'ingaruka z'ubwandu bwari bwihishe aho kuba ubwandu bwongeye kugaruka.
Bivugwa ko iyi virusi ari iy'ibanze kandi ko ikomoka ku nyamaswa, ikwirakwira binyuze mu kwanduzanya.
Inkomoko nyayo ya virusi ntizwi, ariko mu Ukuboza 2019, ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu ryari hafi cyane riyobowe n'ubwandu bw'abantu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 41 ba mbere banduye COVID-19 bwasohotse muri Mutarama 2020 mu kinyamakuru The Lancet, bwagaragaje ko ibimenyetso byatangiye kugaragara bwa mbere ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019.
Ibitabo byemewe na OMS byatangaje ko ibimenyetso byatangiye kugaragara ku itariki ya 8 Ukuboza 2019.
Hari ibintu byinshi bikunze gukoreshwa mu gupima umubare w'abapfa.
Iyi mibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi biganishwa n'umubare w'ibipimo, ubuziranenge bw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe cy'icyorezo, n'ibiranga abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima.
Mu mpera za 2019, OMS yashyizeho kode z'ibiza za ICD-10 U07.1 ku bantu bapfuye bazize kwandura SARS-CoV-2 na U07.2 ku bantu bapfuye bazize COVID-19 kandi nta bwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugaragara. Imibare y'abapfuye igaragaza umubare w'abapfuye ugabanyijwe n'umubare w'abanduye mu gihe runaka.
Imibare ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins igaragaza ko ku itariki ya 17 Mata 2020, imibare y'abamaze gupfa ku isi yose iri ku kigero cya 6.9% (153,822/2 240 191).
Iyi mibare itandukanye bitewe n'akarere. Ibindi bipimo birimo igipimo cy'urupfu (CFR) kigaragaza umubare w'abantu basanganywe uburwayi bapfa kubera uburwayi, n'igipimo cy'urupfu rw'ubwandu (IRF) kigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye (basanganywe uburwayi cyangwa batabufite) bapfa kubera uburwayi.
Iyi mibare ntabwo ihagarariye igihe kandi ikurikirana abaturage runaka kuva ku banduye kugeza ku ndwara irangiye.
Nubwo abantu bose banduye batagira abanduye, kuba hari abanduye bishobora kugaragaza umubare w'abanduye.
Mu mujyi munini w'ubutaliyani urimo icyorezo cya Ebola, Castiglione d'Adda, umudugudu muto utuwe n'abaturage 4600, 80 muri bo (1.7%) baramaze gupfa.
Muri Gangelt, iyi ndwara yageze mu bantu binyuze mu minsi mikuru no mu rubyiruko, bituma hapfa abantu bake cyane, kandi abantu bose bapfuye bazize COVID-19 bashobora kuba batarafatwa nk'abapfuye.
Byongeye kandi, ubuvuzi bw'Abadage ntibwigeze burushaho gukenerwa.
Mu Buholandi, abantu bagera kuri 3 ku ijana bashobora kugira abasirikare b'umubiri, nk'uko bigaragazwa n'igenzura ry'abatanga amaraso.
Abantu 69 bapfuye (0,004% by'abaturage) bemejwe ko barwaye COVID-19.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo n'imfu z'abapfa bitandukanye ku bagabo no ku bagore.
Imfu ziri hejuru mu bagabo mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani.
Ibyago byo kurwara iyi ndwara ni byinshi cyane ku bagabo bafite imyaka 50, aho itandukaniro hagati y'abagabo n'abagore riba ryiyongereye cyane ku myaka 90 gusa.
Mu Bushinwa, igipimo cy'abapfa cyari 2.8% ku bagabo na 1.7% ku bagore.
Impamvu nyayo zituma iryo tandukaniro hagati y'ibitsina bitaramenyekana, ariko hari ibimenyetso byo mu maraso n'imyifatire bishobora kuba biri muri byo.
Itandukaniro ry'ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara hagati y'ibitsina, kuba abagore batanywa itabi cyane, no kuba abagabo barwara indwara ziterwa n'isukari nyinshi mu gihe bakiri bato kurusha abagore, bishobora kuba byaratumye abagabo bapfa cyane.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye bari abagabo, naho 72% by'abahitanywe na COVID-19 bari abagabo.
Muri Mata 2020, leta ya Amerika ntiyakusanyaga amakuru ajyanye n'igitsina cy'abanduye COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu nka Ebola, SIDA, ibicurane na SARS zigira ingaruka zitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Umubare munini w'abakozi b'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, ni abagore kandi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi virusi.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko izina ry'ubuvuzi ry'iyi ndwara ari  COVID-19 .
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yasobanuye ko CO isobanura korona, VI isobanura virusi na D isobanura indwara, 19 ikaba ari yo ya mbere yamenyekanye ko ari icyorezo: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Iri zina ryatoranyijwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda ko hagira aho rivugwa (urugero: Ubushinwa), ubwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, hakurikijwe amabwiriza mpuzamahanga yo gushyiraho amazina agamije kwirinda gutukwa. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa coronavirus 2 ifitanye isano n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV-2).
OS ikoresha kandi  virusi ya COVID-19  na  virusi itera COVID-19  mu itangazamakuru.
Iyo ndwara na virusi byombi bikunze kwitwa  coronavirus .
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabereye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byakundaga kwitwa  coronavirus  na  Wuhan coronavirus .
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yasabye ko hakoreshwa amazina y'imfatakibanza y'indwara 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze kuri virusi n'indwara, hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo mu 2015 yo kwirinda gukoresha ahantu mu mazina y'indwara na virusi.
Amazina yemewe ya COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yasohotse ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Bitewe n'ubushobozi buke bw'imiyoboro isanzwe y'itangwa ry'ibiribwa, hari ababikora mu buryo bwa digitale bandika ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi nk'udupfunyika n'ibice by'imashini z'ubuhumekero.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byasabaga ibyuma byo guhumeka byihutirwa kandi ababikora batabibonaga ku gihe, ikigo cy'aho cyatangiye gukora ibintu by'ikoranabuhanga cyasubiye inyuma maze cyandika ibyuma 100 by'ubuvuzi byasabwaga mu ijoro rimwe.
Nyuma y'aho COVID-19 itangiriye kwibasira abantu, ibitekerezo by'ubuhendanyi, amakuru y'ibinyoma n'amakuru atari yo byatangiye kuvugwa ku nkomoko, ubukana, kwirinda, kuvura n'ibindi bintu by'iyi ndwara, kandi bikwirakwira ku mbuga za interineti mu buryo bwihuse.
Bisa n'aho umuntu ashobora gukwirakwiza iyi ndwara ku zindi nyamaswa.
Ubushakashatsi ntibwigeze bushobora kubona ibimenyetso byerekana ko virusi ishobora kwiyongera mu ngurube, ibitunguru n'inkoko.
Nta muti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe kuvura iyi ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku nkingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 ubu bukorwa n'imiryango ya leta, amatsinda y'abanyeshuri n'abashakashatsi bo mu nganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije  igerageza rya SOLIDARITY  rigamije gusuzuma ingaruka z'imiti ine ya virusi iriho igaragaza ko ifite ubushobozi bwinshi.
Nta rukingo ruhari, ariko inzego nyinshi ziri gukora cyane ku bakandida b'urukingo.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere kuri SARS-CoV burakoreshwa kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'abantu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira bukomeje gushakishwa.
Icya mbere, abashakashatsi barimo kugerageza gukora urukingo rw'agakoko kose.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyi, yaba idafite ubuzima cyangwa yapfuye, bigamije gutuma umubiri w'umuntu uhita ugira ubwirinzi mu gihe umuntu yongeye kwandura COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, inkingo zishingiye ku gice cy'ubwirinzi, bugamije gukora inkingo zituma abasirikare b'umubiri bamenya ibice by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bya virusi.
Ku bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubu bushakashatsi bwibanze kuri poroteyine ya S ifite uruti rw'umugongo ifasha virusi kwinjira mu cyuma cyakira ACE 2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni urukingo rushingiye kuri acide nucléaire (inkingo zifashishije ADN cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo gukora inkingo).
Inkingo zigeragezwa zivuye muri ubwo buryo bwose zigomba kugeragezwa ku bijyanye n'umutekano n'imikorere. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, igeragezwa rya mbere ry'urukingo ryatangiranye n'abakorerabushake bane i Seattle.
Uru rukingo rufite kode y'imiterere itagira icyo itwaye yakuwe kuri virusi itera iyi ndwara. Gushyira mu bikorwa kw'urusobe rw'abasirikare b'umubiri byavuzwe ko bishobora kuba imbogamizi mu gukora urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, ariko biravuguruzanya.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hari ibizamini byo kwa muganga birenga 300 biri gukorwa.
Ibizamini birindwi byasuzumye imiti ya malaria yamaze kwemerwa, harimo n'ibizamini bine byakozwe kuri hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi ni yo ikorwa cyane mu bushakashatsi bw'Abashinwa, harimo igerageza ry'icyiciro cya gatatu rya Remdesivir mu bihugu byinshi, riteganyijwe mu mpera za Mata.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye ku mikoreshereze y'inkingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 na bwo bwariho muri Mata 2020. Hari imiti myinshi ya virusi irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo Remdesivir, Chloroquine na Hydroxychloroquine, Lopinavir/Ritonavir na Lopinavir/Ritonavir ifatanyije na Interferon beta.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko imiti ya remdesivir ishobora gukoreshwa neza muri Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abarwayi bagaragaye ko barushijeho kugira neza mu gihe bahabwa imiti ya remdesivir ikoreshwa mu buryo burangwa n'impuhwe.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga byo mu cyiciro cya gatatu birakomeje muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ibinini bya chloroquine byahoze bikoreshwa mu kuvura malariya byakorewe ubushakashatsi mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, bibonamo ibisubizo bya mbere.
Icyakora, hari bamwe basaba ko ubushakashatsi bwagombye gusesengurwa mu buryo bwigenga.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bw'u Bushinwa n'ubw'u Koreya bwemeza ko iklorokwini ikoreshwa.
Icyakora, ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku ndwara za virusi cyo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nubwo gitanga inama yo gufata igramu imwe ku munsi, kivuga ko iyo umuntu afashe igramu ebyiri ku munsi ari ibintu biteje akaga cyane kandi bishobora kumwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yemeje ikoreshwa rya Hydroxychloroquine na Chloroquine hakurikijwe uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa ku bushake bw'abaganga bita ku barwayi ba COVID-19. Itegeko Nshinga rya 7 ryo mu Bushinwa rinakubiyemo interféron, ribavirine cyangwa Lumifenovir ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'ibanze bigaragaza ko dosiye nyinshi za ribavirine zikenewe mu kubuza SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba.
Nitazoxanide yasabwe gukomeza kwifashishwa mu bushakashatsi bwa in vivo nyuma yo kugaragaza ko ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 mu rugero rwo hasi. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko poroteyine ya mbere ya spicule itangirana na serine transmembrane protease 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ingenzi mu gutuma SARS-CoV-2 yinjira mu mubiri binyuze mu guhura n'urwunganira rwa ACE 2.
Ubushakashatsi ku muti wa chloroquine na lhydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa idafite azithromycin bufite aho bugarukira cyane bituma abaganga batawwemera badafite ubundi bushakashatsi. Loseltamivir ntibubuza SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba kandi nta ruhare ruzwi ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Igitero cy'indwara ya COVID-19 gishobora kuba ikibazo mu gihe cy'indwara ikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya imiterere y'ibinyabutabire. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa nyuma y'ubushakashatsi buto.
Ubu iri mu igeragezwa ry'icyiciro cya 2 mu gihugu hose mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza ko ifite ingaruka nziza ku bantu barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Iyo bifatanyije n'isuzuma ry'amaraso ya ferritin mu maraso kugira ngo hamenyekane igitutu cy'imyakura, bigomba kurwanya izo mpinduka zikekwaho guhitana bamwe mu bantu bayanduye.
Ikoreshwa ry'umuti urwanya interleukin-6 ryemejwe na FDA hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma ku buvuzi bwo kuvura indwara y'ubwiyongere bw'imikorere ya sitokine zitemera siteroyi ziterwa n'impamvu itandukanye, ni ukuvuga imiti ya CAR T cells, mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya na kimwe cyakozwe mu buryo butunganijwe neza kigaragaza ko tocilizumab ari umuti mwiza wa SCR.
Kwimura abasirikare barwanya COVID-19 bakoresheje ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bw'abantu bakize COVID-19 bakabishyira mu bantu babikeneye birimo gusuzumwa nk'uburyo butari ubwisungane mu gukingira abantu.
Ubu buryo bwakozwe mu gupima SARS nta byavuyeho byinshi.
Gukuraho virusi ni uburyo bwitezwe bwo kuvura butuma imiti ikoreshwa mu kurwanya virusi itera SIDA ituma umuntu arwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, hari ubundi buryo bushobora kubaho, urugero nk'ubwandu bw'umubiri mu ngirabuzimafatizo bushingiye ku basirikare n'ubundi bwitwa phagocytosis.
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kuvura indwara ziterwa n'imiti, urugero nko gukoresha abasirikare b'umubiri b'umwimerere, buri gukorwa.
Imikorere ya serumu y'abarwayi bakize, igizwe n'igice cy'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize gifite abasirikare ba virusi, ishobora kwiyongera kugira ngo ikwirakwizwe vuba.
